m/a/ACg8ocJd2yLF2X7iquzrtzLUJ_NpNeenRarraxO1yrUZ8EpjW6UhiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Shih gave me the best cleaning that I’ve ever had! He was very informative, knowledgeable, and gentle with his work. Thank you Dr Shih and the rest of the office/clinical staff for making my experience so memorable! I highly recommend coming here!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sheila sena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXy0ite-6D_XDk_4s4Q0IKRWyaP8A1eeNuxefL4j3Vh0xUtIDC5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Lake Washington Dental!\nI had my teeth cleaned by Dr. Moazami, and it was a great experience. She was very punctual, provided very clear explanations, and the clinic has a calm and welcoming atmosphere. I felt well cared for from start to finish! Dr. Débora, her assistant, is also very professional and competent.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lVX81kkUGyEYZHPsPYloUyXjjv1DBtOzsFQUil22cR3_5RA8DIQgGpMciNnb_o0G5mdCWMENwLwNEOXu-hmKnzwPvPmDvJ8aCy5usbApdx5v1WPejdBJGB-wLJI8t3PGzkD8T0QPcSbaX=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-4"},{"Name":"Stephanie Dye","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkvpOVpl-7MgyD-TljG_5DL9pHUkNQzA97jFW2f9Si5oq_sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a t,errible toothache the day before new years eve. The receptionist got me in, Dr Mo got me some antibiotics and we made a plan for the new year. Office staff are always helpful. Dr. Mo is very skilled, I feel very safe. Highly recommended,  especially for the more complex problems.\nThank you, Stephanie Dye","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Neiliane Depaulaalcantra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_q0EghmQbpGE45N929vjKfedJ26eDfZ0d4Fj89Y8HUHjZz10=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved everyone, they were all very attentive to me. The person who works at the reception is a great person; even though I don't speak the language very well, she helped me with everything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Lum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFeKjmY-41HdijLIxDTUXMJ06QxO49JbgNn9XAm_fLYwDo1Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Moazami evaluated my bite when I fell on a walk last August. Her initial diagnosis was a fractured jaw and that I will need to immediately go to ER for further examination by an oral specialist.  The arch bars in my mouth were removed after 4.5 months.  I made an appointment with Dr. Moazami for a dental cleaning and see what needs too be done on chipped tooth from the fall. She recommended to do a root canal and crown.  In several months. She has been fabulous and highly recommend her for all your dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jonathanopugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWswjs8dXfsUHM6HEAjtbba4wKk7A7nJN5yBvirrs_rIW0G5fIJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a brand new member of the LakeWashington dental clinic and I must say I made the best choice after searching Google for the top five dentists in our area. Dr. Mo is an expert in her field and was so personable and caring about all things relating to my current status.Her receptionist along with her dental assistant that took full set of x-rays are superior! After the x-rays, Dr. Mo proceeded to clean my teeth with one of the most pain-free experiences I can remember! She really has a way of putting any anxiety you may have at ease and recommends just the right plan for your future dental healthcare. In conclusion, I told her that because of my experience with her and her staff  that she could go ahead and give herself a raise!😎","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jessica perez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSXrcHzfsEw-kDPFFv2sFMGmX4e8RNnpyBPBLaGykziTum5U4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best cleaning I have ever received at a dental office! Very informative too on concerns and questions I asked. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"cindy mcdonough","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIO934ctGEhE_7ORAt2zknj7xO1IIomMNkMYfIG0eDNzBzcWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Shih is the best!! I should know my ex- husband was a dentist!! Dr. Shih is gentle with firm hands. My gums are super sensitive and I appreciate he doesn’t hurt then during a cleaning.  My teeth are sparkling white when he is finished. I fully trust him- he is the best Dentist!.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
