alse}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Tigran Bayburtski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnnpp0mi5eBG3zl1OXX_rHHx_WkGX5MLOTKnGllmKSSu-fBQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my first appointment today and couldn’t be happier! Everyone was so kind and professional—the front desk greeted me warmly, the hygienist was gentle and thorough, and the dentist answered all my questions patiently. Felt completely at ease the whole time. Highly recommend this practice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raphael Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQVe0EX4Ecsxj8q67JFryRNVi8chFplIwguueInK4Nu2MQt4E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience here! Everyone was super friendly and made me feel comfortable. I had a cleaning and a filling done, and both were quick, easy, and done with care. Shout out to Dr. Tsen and Cira!  Definitely recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ellie boone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7mKe6jo1L5Vi-axkg-uKmyJAOJf5nclRU3TJp09AG7aj_TSUq=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot praise Dr. Tsen enough! He is amazing along with the rest of the Gentle Dental team. I don't think I have ever had a dentist be so kindhearted, professional and make me feel so comfortable during any dental work. He listens to your concerns, walks you through the process and continues to check in to see how you are feeling. If you are someone who gets really nervous about going to the dentist, Dr. Tsen is the person to go to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jeremy Poling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6VAAPSfjCumA2WqPjutNsvSYux-6HTamN_QWhBsw7U_4hEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really glad we decided to get a second opinion! We had already been to one orthodontist, but something just didn’t feel right. Came here and the difference was night and day. We walked out knowing this was where we wanted my daughter to get her treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ladina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUSGrmF9RE290zevzbpTV-b_cKqql9e6h8SzPzGH0bcqrAz5hz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Thank you for the kind and positive attitudes from the Dr and assistant, hygienist. I will be recommending your office. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebekah Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhLIMNA2aJm1txBGg6uneQPyLqdhIaRmC_ZrnWvAQy9Kj95w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love the experience and care Dr. Tsen provides. He is always so detailed and thoughtful in explaining every step of the way what he is doing. He listens and is always patient in answering any questions. He's kind, professional and outstanding in dental care. The entire team is always so warm and welcoming and also very professional. Feeling really grateful for all the staff here. Brenda\nCira and Karen at the front desk. Appreciate each of you and your commitment to providing kind and professional service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Van Valkenburgh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK_6376vRPUbaP0Ooi8V9dWis458PhiC1iZfswi_pR5MmYAKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As pain free as one could ever expect. In and out quickly, efficiently and proficiently.\nSera is the definition of cheerful, bordering on bubbly. ;-)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandeep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGvVH-8_Rvv8iMKfweCtJPUv25mQYcEGvSoxFR83NAtMu9GQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Very unethical. They were not clear about billing and charges. They sent a bill to collections and even started adding interest, even though it wasn’t our fault. The quality of service also got worse. We have moved away from Gentle Dental.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
