Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a wonderful experience here! The office is very clean and organized, and everyone on the staff is so kind and welcoming. Dr. Sheena did an amazing job on my front two crowns—they look so natural that no one can tell they aren’t my real teeth. I used to feel insecure about my smile for the longest time, but now I can finally smile with confidence, and I constantly get compliments on how great my teeth look. I’m so thankful for Dr. Sheena and her amazing team, and I’m so happy I found this place!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xUHJQ0zJWBC4yuUC_K6pTlW2dKQ0UskMUTdTi_S9z1q-Jjd1V0V4gpMwT4wUuvAtNCT2O-pi-vq0bLc_qHZQoqdqruKLB4ku_SIEaUFOpf5Gd8bAYMtVaDcceUk63VdMiSrb1l_q3Ok0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Z9LEpIIhhnnzHK80eRWEanOz0jQSxxtV0rHtPLb29NATJz7MQ8FyrsP_u3SXAjpxdoAyoXmWp6IV24eyiuCD-bU4E9UKxvROQhO96Yr1_iKMwII09fne_9kfQIvTOHxwuJTc0ml-xK1Y=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-26"},{"Name":"Scot Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkweKgOBFJW-dWy9T5gRTpQdi1UgSwSa91IjO5aW4rSGtSz-8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Stars! Kirkland Premier Dentistry have been outstanding for both my wife and myself. They really go above and beyond to make us feel comforted and supported. The dental procedures, including a Crown and Invisaline, have been perfect. Keep up the great work, Kirkland Premier Dentistry!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Simmons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRIXX_aCfVnW6fdXdPvh3zrOjWoIlEHbgrA11XVCdrGMWItv4p=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are amazing. The whole staff was helpful and friendly. I was able to get in same day and had two wisdom teeth pulled. It was quick and pain free as much as possible. Highly recommended. Will be returning to have my other two wisdom teeth removed. And a crown finished. Great place that care about their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karla Delreal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLN4lCDheKXR3uwVMHY2SYrSoXM9dHTIF7vk1J4cOoxpVjmnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sure! Here’s a professional, friendly, and helpful dentist review. If you want it to sound more personal, detailed, or tailored to a specific situation (e.g., a cleaning, emergency, or cosmetic procedure), let me know.\n\n⸻\n\n⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️ 5/5 Stars\n\nI had a fantastic experience at Kirkland premier dentistry  From the moment I walked in, the staff was welcoming, professional, and made me feel completely at ease. The office was clean, modern, and well-organized, which immediately gave me confidence in the level of care they provide.\n\nDr. Sharma was incredibly thorough, explaining each step of the exam and answering all my questions patiently. I appreciated their gentle approach and the time they took to ensure I was comfortable throughout the appointment. Even the cleaning was surprisingly pleasant!\n\nWhat stood out most was the genuine care and attention to detail. I never felt rushed, and it was clear that patient comfort and quality care are a top priority here.\n\nHighly recommend to anyone looking for a trustworthy, skilled, and kind dental team. I’ll definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeff Rafuse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRpiM5uhCfbALX8NBvEcDP9mkWYHZ1914YP1FqjqYAmbEHaCU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son had a minor dental emergency with his braces over the weekend while his orthodontist was closed and Kirkland Premier Dentistry was so accommodating to get him in quickly (same day on a Saturday!) - even as a new patient. Even though this was an orthodontics issue, they were happy and able to address the problem in a way so it’s no longer an emergency. The front desk staff, doctor and his assistant were  all so friendly. I’m thankful for having a business in our community like this.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shrikant Jaiswal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVY4qjyxqXuV3rCske_M_FG3nsrilhDbmpFFsnUsOSw9wBLIwSy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my dental implant by Dr. Gaurav Sharma. I did not feel any pain during procedure and almost no swelling or discomfort afterwards. The entire team was caring and welcoming, I will recommend this team for anyone needing oral surgery. Thanks to the caring team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ravish Khanna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ60cLs9RSAai5FX0fnGyeY42Kjj8FsayD5Ijj1ZhUoipuqvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with the doctors and and their team at Kirkland Premier Dentistry. I went in to get a filling fixed, and they made the whole process quick, painless, and comfortable. Dr was gentle, explained everything clearly, and made sure I was at ease the entire time. My tooth feels perfect now—no pain or sensitivity at all. The staff were friendly and professional from start to finish. Highly recommend this office for anyone looking for a trustworthy and caring dentist","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hector Castaneda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWAFvQWCYNSdohVLB2MaeBrF8rnybe1YVLAO-Pb3NDm6am75xc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such an amazing experience at this dental office! The entire team was professional, friendly, and made me feel completely comfortable from the moment I walked in. Dr. Jaskiran Kaur took the time to explain everything clearly and was incredibly gentle throughout my treatment. The office is spotless, modern, and runs right on schedule — no long waits. I actually left smiling (literally and figuratively)! Highly recommend Dr. Jaskiran Kaur and their team to anyone looking for a dentist who truly cares about their patients!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
