 favorite dental office! The staff are always friendly, professional, and knowledgeable. Dr. Hsue and Dr. Fredrickson are both excellent, and Virginia is my favorite dental hygienist.  She’s gentle, thorough, and always makes me feel comfortable. Jocelyn, the dental assistant, is very helpful and ensures I have a great experience during my procedures. Cindy and Melissa are so welcoming and kind from the moment you arrive until the time you leave. Cindy has even gone out of her way to help me resolve insurance issues. I highly recommend Annigan Dental to anyone looking for outstanding dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Diana Водолей","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ_4RzSI2TZzuN4T1aPTg71wKJTDdzu3pHH9wrNyi6Uqp2f4w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to this clinic for over 4 years now. They have a great team, starting with Melissa, who is always attend ready to help at the reception desk. And also excellent doctors Hsue and Fredrickson, who are very friendly, work carefully and quickly, and are always ready to explain all possible treatment options. I truly feel that they care about their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emily","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzyGLQrjpOZhnlBPHSy0D-zStjjAx6gXZY9ymm6-LINV2awg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been coming here for about 3 years now for both regular cleanings and orthodontics, and it’s always a great experience. The staff \u0026 doctors are seriously all so friendly, patient, super helpful, knowledgeable \u0026 trustworthy. They are always willing to help with flexibility in scheduling, payment inquiries, and plenty of options for whatever you’re needing. The facilities are always clean and the atmosphere is lovely. Also, Melissa at the front desk is the nicest person ever. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Toves","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaL5V3IHKyUjKuhZpxE2qu2bhVWzmpqycKuFWt0-uKIIYjhw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the BEST place to do all of your dental, especially if you suffer from DENTAL ANXIETY like I do!!! Of all the offices I've ever visited, this was the least nervous I had ever felt as soon as I checked into my first appointment. I had a terrible tooth infection for a while most likely and was in alot of pain when I visited. They were quick to assess me and start on treatment asap, which was nice considering the amount of pain i had. Then they were thorough explaining the plan of action to me and they were very accommodating with my needs. Most of all, they are very gentle \u0026 attentive with me every step of the way physically! Dr. Hsue, his assistants, even the operations manager at the front desk all make me feel like they're on my side with me!! Like they care and like i can truly trust in them! That makes ALL the difference! MVP team roster! 10/10 experience every time! Annigan Dental is #1!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KJ Chan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLreYVDUhMg7dZABvnzNa9FU5aD319qbg5Z3bNRH6oyxxTpYrv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentist is impressive! He is not only able to analyze complex situation but also able to develop a good solution plan to work on your whole mouth. He treated my left side and show me what is the best way to work the right side of tooth. The whole process will take about a yr but i can already tell my teeth condition is getting much better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuGCdy8KU9Bws1Ds46kWTl8_oqGZshewoJHcF13Zj_loMZ2Ag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Avoid this dental office – they prioritize profit over patient care.\n\nI was a patient here for three years, and from the very beginning, they kept pressuring me to get a crown, even though my tooth pulp was still healthy. Every visit, they pushed the same recommendation. I repeatedly declined and asked for a filling instead.\n\nLast month, my filling fell out, so I returned to have it replaced. The filling was still under warranty, but they refused to honor it simply because I had declined the crown. They gave me two options: 1) Pay $1,000 out of pocket for a crown, or 2) Pay $500 for a new filling with no warranty coverage.\n\nThis clearly shows they care more about money than their patients' well-being.\n\nI decided to seek a second opinion at another dental office. The new dentist confirmed that my tooth is still in good condition and that I won't need a crown for at least another 10 years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lindy Briggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNhgk7lXlwfJt1ha_m-4JAWcqjF7O9a8XBgukUYg1P7nf4he8zvA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I interviewed a few dentists before I landed on Annigan and I've loved their work. They're easy to work with and Dr. Frederickson has a real eye for technique and detail. Thank you for everything, guys! And thank you for being patient with your patient!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amir Ab","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3e1VBI2sruLUibUpaebzAA8KN3FuBhG58Qjc1COB8zrzxtKjd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great staff and treatment.\nAs a new patient, I find everything high standards and meeting the expectations.\nDr is super amazing provides consultations before starting his work/treatment.\nThe staff are super professional, friendly, and quick.\nGreat materials are provided for patients.\n\nKids receive some toys and treats.\nFree snacks and non alcoholic beverages provided.\n\nOverall I have great experience and so happy for my decision.\n\nThank you for providing great customer satisfaction","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2p6BuLmJtDTWgQMhhcheAw-tk8eTw7j2QKRthvUI_d83v5NCBBaLb8lHva8-0l9rQDPF3BtA7qD6Df0uGu8k_8lm6d