d":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Mariana Carrola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLos8rtvT5GTJ1g9w4r_V300iWSaE8aOkc4mTxZJaJBPh641A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience! Dr Ament and all the staff are professional and kind. They really care about your well-being and take the time to answer questions. Pain-free and efficient procedures. I highly recommend them—my entire family trusts this place. If you’re looking for a dentist office this is your place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan White","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyQuQPOjoLgYebUjGQRvpYUuZrFNM4E9HczMxTAjqkYJoXNXvJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone is incredibly kind and friendly, along with being gentle and efficient with their work. Dr. Ament is very cognizant of any past dental anxiety, and provides a clear treatment plan with your input. Dr. Ament's pup Koda is a delightful bonus.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackie Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJamqRRpl76eAzlkeju14pbqV3ZNL9Rr1_T3vdcVWZEYS53yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience today as a new patient at Bothell Family Dentistry! Everyone on the team was warm and welcoming throughout the process and I was really impressed with Dr. Ament.\nSpecial shout outs to Destiny who gave me the best teeth cleaning experience I’ve ever had and to Kayla who brings a warm, friendly approach on the phone and in person!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sabrina Berkman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjr2teHHGXUUztRdG986U4wRu6fCoW-G_vDdf6t22H6JDolB4z=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone in the office was so kind, and patient with me. I have a lot of dental anxiety, and they made the experience so comfortable. Koda, the office dog is so fun and a joy to play with. Destiny, the hygienist was so gentle and an absolute joy to chat with. The dentist was very clear about my care plan and gave me plenty of autonomy while also steering me in a good direction. I will be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R Saleira","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKba1kPBG4ObCbPmIIrCtQGPiuNp5YQd4VyNO0fuvXoFcwQYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a cavity filled at this office, and I can't say enough good things about my experience. Dr. Ament and her staff were incredibly friendly and highly professional, creating a welcoming atmosphere from the moment I walked in until my procedure was complete. And let's not forget their adorable therapy dog!\n\nAs my visit also required an emergency procedure, I was especially grateful that they addressed my concerns on the same day. It's clear that they genuinely care about their patients' comfort, and the quality of their work is outstanding. They truly make dental visits so much easier!\n\nI also appreciate that this office is equipped with state-of-the-art instruments and has an easy-to-navigate website, allowing patients to communicate effortlessly without having to wait for a callback. Overall, a fantastic experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andre Booker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMHSnkuECm-rTv1carJgU9aIqOwkhYwNDj706xMorXRC4tjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I always enjoy my trips to Bothell Family Dentistry, this visit however, I had the pleasure of meeting Destiny.  Who, like myself, is a Navy Vet.  She was better than wonderful.  She was very personable and made this visit great.  I also would be remiss r if I didn’t mention the entire staff.  At 730 in the morning they are already in afternoon form.  I love this office and the ladies that make it go.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Kremer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViuk5TIkyun60Q-Ub85FG6QB8SXtrs9o6OnPnYbBrUNWSrAV2H=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ament and her staff are amazing. Front desk was friendly, hygienists were gentle and kind, and Dr. Ament is so knowledgeable and was quick to educate me \u0026 offer solutions for dental insecurities I’ve had my whole life. I’ve never had a dentist take such care to not only ask, but also listen. And the cutie office dog is a happy bonus!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelsey Murfitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjTKG98P__u82VlfY0gB-na_WZCqOgpii3ZPIBszqiTPI1-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m a newer patient of Dr. Ament and Bothell Family Dentistry. As someone with a history of dental anxiety, I was very worried coming back to the dentist after some time away, knowing there would be some significant work to be done. Over the last few months, I’ve been so grateful for the thorough, empathetic and compassionate care from Dr. Ament, her hygienists, assistants and all her staff. Would highly recommend this practice to anyone, but particularly those of us with dental anxiety from subpar past experiences.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
