ncy services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"David Moon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXR6duUZPeX-xbFZsfn-WmDEzIow3Yf7U052wusQP7w0s0JmI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I visited Hope Dental for a root canal treatment and crown procedure. The clinic was exceptionally clean, bright, and well organized, with a modern and welcoming environment. All staff members were courteous, friendly, and professional, which made the experience very comfortable.\n\nDr. Moon demonstrated a high level of expertise and professionalism. He accurately identified the issue and clearly explained the diagnosis using X-ray images. He thoroughly outlined the treatment plan and the procedures required to resolve the problem. Throughout each stage of the treatment, Dr. Moon worked carefully and efficiently, successfully completing both procedures.\n\nAfter the treatment, he took the time to explain what had been done, what to expect during recovery, and provided clear guidance on how to care for my tooth. He also answered all of my questions in a clear and reassuring manner.\n\nOverall, my experience at Hope Dental was extremely positive. I highly recommend Hope Dental to anyone seeking professional, knowledgeable, and compassionate dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Robert Fowler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXskfMLy2RMID43MbczGuubDTfKh8I4IqDj5SaVCCySaJ5WVTyF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been coming here for a couple years now and just finished getting a molar implant put in. They've done an excellent job with all of the dental work. The receptionist has been especially helpful in working with me to figure out my insurance and how to schedule things so that I would pay the least out of pocket. Highly recommend Hope Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKF_62df2145rQscb0OzP2hOxmu51llEcPj0GyJ7uxDezN3Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every staffs are so kind and makes comfort.\nI had regular teeth cleaning. Thanks for Ruth, she was very thoughtful and did very carefully because I suffered TMJ. Dr. Moon is awesome and supportive for my condition.\nThanks again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sydney Chang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg3m-a6QeuBH4nZaLiotsCaMaBZ26pe4u-9gTO1t4px4ktmLI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone is very nice here. Dr. Moon was very gentle and  told me everything he was doing during my cleaning. The facility is super clean. My best dentist experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pikmin Tailor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5bYEDeY08ylxuEeVv_eN7HtZiWau2ZaJAmp0_UK2-t9NEFEll=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place was super good!! All the staff were super nice and helpful!! I was able to make my appointment less than an hour before coming in, and I initially came came in for an exam to see my wisdom teeth checked out, but they also ended up giving me a cleaning and a referral for orthodontics and the oral surgeon for my wisdom teeth extraction! Super sweet and it was my first dentist appointment in years so it’s for sure going to be my next go-to spot!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"marilyn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4NAZdUPRj_0GeWkhnUCUHW0LewBxrKWOYs2epPK