age":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=z6aoBLYFDmo_0r92QsF9ag\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=291.78564\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://www.lynnwooddentalcenter.com/lynnwood-dental-appointment.html","source":"lynnwooddentalcenter.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"111572875089792727461","name":"Lynnwood Dental Excellence (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111572875089792727461"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"4202 198th St SW Suite 3","city":"Lynnwood","postal_code":"98036","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"from_the_business","name":"From the business","options":[{"name":"Identifies as Asian-owned","enabled":true},{"name":"Identifies as women-owned","enabled":true}]},{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true},{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"habtamu michael","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIFnehgKb7e7o3gHubNfsFCCgO9x36m9RzSIlw3NPcQO2IFp0_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m very happy with the service I received. The staff was friendly and welcoming, and the doctor was extremely nice and professional. I felt comfortable throughout the visit, and my tooth problem was clearly explained and treated. Thank you for the great care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mimi Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7c09j8WXVqNozbU6Dy4B4LIWJrUl3KjqoRMQxnLQz1Iur4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first implant that I had done somewhere else is not working well, so seeing that Dr Yeh at Lynnwood Dental Excellence is the only one of the few in the States that is board certified for dental implants give me the peace of mind that I will be well taken care of. Dr Yeh has good skills and excellent knowledge in his field.  I will definitely be going back for my next few implants and other dental work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matthew Hodge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKjskLYcRzNoBwV45OKIhbfpHjX0L13enK_F_tgEL_-A-YqNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of visiting Lynnwood Dental Excellence for the first time yesterday, and I can't recommend it enough! From the moment I walked in, the staff was friendly and welcoming. But the real standout was Julia, the hygienist. Hands down the best cleaning I've ever had. She was so thorough yet gentle, making sure I was comfortable every step of the way. Julia's attention to detail was incredible. She made sure to address everything and I learned a lot from her during my visit. Not only that, but she’s genuinely fun to chat with, which made the whole experience even better. I’ve never felt so relaxed during a dental cleaning! If you're looking for top-notch care with a personal touch, this is the place. I booked my next appointment prior to leaving.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Damon Diener","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg3QYwRnOYDKot4BdTTLcC3Pu2bJ7wg67REJ8ECeBaUivfwA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Received a tooth Extraction and filling with Dr. Jackie. She was very kind and worked late to make sure she got my procedure done. It was smooth for the most part and everyone was very respectful and helpful. Definitely would recommend in a time of need to check them out!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SUNDARESWARA SIVARATNAM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpplU-lZoBZB2sgbX2dCtsmGZhC0bvWCZGrVMre92_awCozQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As I had many questions concerning my dental care \u0026 restoration of my tooth the services provided namely the front desk associate \" SMITHA \" was awesome. Her explanation to my numerous questions \u0026 concerns related to my dental care were answered to great satisfaction.\nHer patience with politeness with accuracy in detail was amazing.  She is a very articulate person in dealing with people which is a great asset to this dental care facility.  Thanks very much for all your help \" SMITHA \" and wish you the very best on your career endeavors.\nSunda Sivaratnam - potential patient as seeking second opinion from this dental care facility.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sarah marangon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVQ9BwCIbb2YuoraCWBaZKxylhzstFIlGktX_Lrn_Hgxcw82LA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If you only need a basic teeth cleaning, this place is fine. If you need a cavity filled—DO NOT do it. Get a second opinion.\n\nI went in for a routine cleaning and was told I had two cavities and that they could fill them immediately. My teeth weren’t bothering me at all, but I figured I might as well fix them before they started to hurt.\n\nAfter they filled the cavities, my teeth were extremely sensitive for the next month. I couldn’t eat anything even remotely hard on the left side. On top of that, every time I flossed, the gums around the filled cavities bled like crazy.\n\nI went back and saw a different dentist, who had to fix their work. He told me the pain should last a few weeks. Well, here I am two months later and I still can’t chew anything hard on the left side. I floss every single day, and the gums around that cavity still bleed a lot.\n\nTo make things worse, I moved to California, so I can’t even go back to have them fix it again—not that I would ever want to. Now I’m stuck paying out of pocket at a new dentist to fix the damage Lynnwood Dental Excellence caused. Extremely frustrating and not okay.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel McLeod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMriYkSF2Ru_oSsMBYJSuQOGSyhExzs86nkUpM4qSu7CZpRHpQrg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is AMAZING! Don't let the older looking building fool you - its definitely not like other fancy offices but they are truly excellent where it matters.\n\nI've only had amazing experiences with the hygienist.  They are all great at what they do.  However just this past week I went in for tooth pain. I saw Dr. Nguyen and low an behold, they took my xrays quickly saw the crack down the middle and upon exam found an infection. The recommendation was an extraction. What im used to is an exam then several follow-up visits before anything really happens. Or a referral to a specialist.  In a matter of 3 hours I got my tooth pulled,  and implant placed in!!!!\n\nDr. Nguyen was incredibly knowledgeable while also training a newer dentist at the same time. Every step of the way he communicated everything, answered all my questions and took the time to listen.\n\nThank you Dr. Nguyen and the team! Also - the front desk gal who went over the cost and quotes is awesome and just so funny.\n\nThank you Lynnwood Dental Excellence!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Simon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpwuKTSfDnmgU68OPdtNXkfiQGbw47C32tXPfg0-gbxc_xnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a great experience with Lynnwood btyDental — honestly one of the smoothest dental visits I’ve ever had. Scheduling was super easy, everything ran on time, and the whole process just felt really straightforward. The staff was incredibly friendly and welcoming, which made the whole thing way less stressful. Overall, just a really positive experience that made going to the dentist feel easy.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
