=175.2647\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://book.modento.io/lakeviewsmiles","source":"modento.io"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"117655338283390650651","name":"Lakeview Smiles Family Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117655338283390650651"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"5701 NE Bothell Way #5","city":"Kenmore","postal_code":"98028","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Bekka Coakley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWSsCdnGXhmXlqLFg9aSViAJoxbRAlfjwKt2sDhETbNkvsuI-mW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lin is so gentle and very communicative about what she’s doing. Her staff are all so friendly and helpful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Yeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrf1T4Ea3qtIMoQw4d48_hsJFgj3LYnfYxXCdtCWe4w6IRl1JVqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going now for a couple years. No issues.  Showed up on time to most recent appointment and found the hygienist running about 20 minutes behind.  Staff was apologetic.  But what really made me write this review was the dentist acknowledged the lateness, apologized and gave me an electric toothbrush.  I'll be honest it wasn't so much the value of the toothbrush but more the fact that they understood my time was valuable and made an effort to compensate me that truly struck me.  Kudos to Lakeview Smiles for understanding the customers point of view and being willing to back it up.  We all get that things happen and being on time doesn't always happen.  But never have I come across a dentist or medical professional who has made an effort to make things right when they're running late.  This customer centric view and honesty will keep me going back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carol Lyons","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT1Nn4cHwVKlwH1GaqSdckzhMOK8J4R_Pduoa_Ialm6cMvj_28=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lin is very friendly and personable; she even remembered our conversation about my family from my visit six months ago! She is extremely thorough and professional, taking care during the exam to make sure I was comfortable and nothing was bothering me. She answered all my questions and took her time to explain procedures, describe x-rays and pictures, and helpful tips for follow-up care at home. The interactions I had with front desk and dental staff were personable and professional too. I felt they took every precaution to keep me safe and made me feel welcome and comfortable at Lakeview Smiles. The office had two new pieces of equipment for imaging that are state-of-the art. A very positive experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lilian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoMPUQKcKYnHpth1cMcbTVeRyAkEoZpcl3vTpxEGMnjRtmig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lin and Cindy were so gentle and attentive that they helped me get my teeth cleaned smoothly even though I had neuralgia. I am very grateful for that.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Virginia Noss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJ-rP-3-BeFY6Xs0tnu2H_90dW183MhzuZmaotQh7Y-LYv8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Doctor Carol Lin  always gave a thorough and professional exam.\nShe is gentle and cares for her patients.\nAll of her office staff are friendly and well organized .\nTheir office meets the strong COVID-19 safety measures for her staff and patients.\nI am also happy with my dental cleaning.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tim Matte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDPdb1jn9tD-56wt8U_qW9-iWn8Dv44To78FtyqhCdjRtg6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very happy with my visits to the office. Dr.Lin takes the time to be with patients, ensuring that all treatment is explained in detail. Very trustworthy. The staff is friendly, everyone works well together. If you are seeking dental attention, Definitely give this office a try.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Winnie Lau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLhOu7gMWIhMzozqTKOIrmfihwfMgABxlC9eyKW0lLeXDl6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful experience here. The staff was very polite and professional. Diana and Dr. Lin were very gentle and caring. Looking forward to my next appointment. Plus, can't beat that view of Lake Washington!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marellen H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTwnmzl-6NJn9I1qf0XditAEAmSQ0VYPgpN8NVUYRAkGpJpbM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Dr. Carol Lin as a second opinion after having a bad experience with my previous dentist. Dr. Lin was not aware of this however, I just told her that I was looking to establish care. Highly recommend this family dentist! She suggested alternative options that better suited my needs in comparison to my previous dentist.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
