ouse. I recommend going to a dentist where they put a temp crown on and get you a quality one.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn39sxdcnGhjQYMJnMSdkzatbuDRIDkbLMt5YUXlEkEyUoOqfGTPFfO-JZB4xMwszytIabQPUjCYBZwGWUE8-fYIEFMfqY_9aq8z79DBXdBVO40CNckfazrOMCJmiNrWvWWI0vKfRCCh2QQW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1aM981Uv_dT4ndtZT11aF9-8RvZgKS6K3Xrqv4IomT-lHmsT-KPvUKmn5-3BQTIGb14Rmw8666h9nP2xwokhYUxpML5Dw-OTHYvcreoOjV4y8WOZEFlT3-ziJelnU-evM0LWKihxhFq39s=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Bv67-l0s8xE77hUE3Bx0S618A1Hf86sheZHWl-mrpRy6INB9memq_qG89UsDNfRh8VZ2nLkGSArzB35O3VcECIwyVnWlf4Tvur48caIFSqiAVH1CSZ9UmZ2QZiOHAwkTSqov23NihZYAD=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-19"},{"Name":"Jason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs0_A8Cl4UmYHM-6Q9GkoIv30W71_JGJkMvWLu6lJ-CovSkQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It’s so convenient that I was able to make an appointment on Saturday. During the weekend it is very difficult to take time off from work. thank you for your great work! the staff is very professional. Leila made me feel very comfortable every time she cleans my teeth. Thank you for your service","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3IUfKE1gKlJQ4ZP4e6XIsbkPaPfLKO2k12HJwnszZs5rc_1EMWShvQfTw2wmJ5n4nrvOWUyRNSvTQBLovsvDSOQnvux99K9f74_o9GEovjubZclr5fVkrsgvmj8tx3zTyfx1PweIXMywVk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2d9eQbtJ6NshVbHvNK8vXVDiZAAtaUicAqsvZtkmIf9aa3kbYHxLXzzMI3KI5QC7cfeUOZ2IdMzzWVXQkpA-ZfDCs8ni2ji8FKOSZVbWG9o5_wU8JkuTi-CCjMDmryyQZEeWT4W6I68A4=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-11"},{"Name":"Judy Winslow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmMyScS2npVRPUGQWE9EiwCn2cEdevn42NKnG_FurvYWhkUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the third dentist I have been to in 6 months and I am so Happy to find them!  Dr Sarah and Suzzie are taking such good care of my dental health.  They have been transparent about charges and take my Medicare Advantage as in network.\n\nDr Sarah is very clear and straight forward in her explanations and visuals , and I Trust her\n\nThey make in house crowns with just a short wait to have them finished in a couple hours at most. Wonderful place and people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiana H.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIda84J9YVns1NokE6uKkkUdOkaKHvSbH1IHRXkc3WmX8iGWMc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my second visit to this dentist, and it was just as amazing as the first! The entire process was smooth and easy, from check-in to the end of the appointment. Dr. Sarah and Sophia are my dentists, and i can’t thank them enough for the great experience. Not only are they professional but also incredibly friendly, which made me feel completely comfortable and at ease the whole time. I definitely recommend this place!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dominique Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-xr7mhUqp3aEJ4L83GS9dtu7Ib67iPJuikedorljJfSoameEAgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My kids and I have been going to  Dr Byun and his team for over 7 years. These guys never stop working their magic. I've had extensive dental work done including several crowns. Every time I go in they check for visible decay and make sure my crowns are sucure. Never have I been mislead, and I've had zero issues. Recently I went in for a small filling and per usual my experience and their expertise was on point. I love these guys,  and hope that I can continue my treatment there.\nDr Byun is very knowledgeable, personable  and gentle. Its very clear that he takes pride in his work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Avery Lycke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL11B4TEhoZ59k6zMdUQvtginpBrVWBpU_xI1lNhnBHRGPx=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Zee the Routine Dental Hygienist at Lynnwood Crossroads Modern Dentistry has cleaned my teeth the last year.\n\nThey were cleaned so well, And the Instruction for Proper Brushing was so clear; I was able to rid myself of peridontis on this most recent visit.\n\nThe Implants the team set at Lynnwood Crossroads Modern Dentistry have also been fantastic. My smile has never looked better!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Renny Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUZdP6EGvj4OTj1lp1fB0ATfaFP3aL0D5Gnoz2PMXIykLQFwjK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time back into a dentists office in years. I was very concerned about my teeth and overall health. The staff was outstanding. Everyone truly cares for their patients. In our current world of fast paced work slowly being replaced with AI, it's reassuring to see that kindness and humanity cannot be replaced. Everyone was amazing, my examination started shortly after getting checked in. They were efficient and the examination was quick and informative. Dr. Byun was exceptionally professional and throughly covered all of my concerns. The actual dental work took about an hour to fix several years of missed cleaning. My usual experiences at the dentist's office is a lot of discomfort and pain but with my experience of Lynnwood Crossroads Modern Dentistry, the staff prioritize their patients with compassion and kindness. Definitely my best experience at a dentist's visit.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
