ob my my teeth.  Highly recommend Caring Family Dentistry!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda McLi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWqG8vzFcUBF6oZ4jA-u13uGQfVujDs6_-NgjCddR_w9vfJxwTz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'd like to express my appreciation for the folks at Caring Family Dentistry after 10+ yrs of great service and a range of dental work!  I've been coming back even after moving away from the area.  Prompt/efficient service, very nice staff \u0026 fun/easy to chat, and seriously great care after an incident that required more involved procedures.  Cheers and thanks.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"david smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5Ie2DDbDLFK900cNTcIy3SwMkDiR5eQRi9b6bcR9rS0Rf2g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you need a dentist in Mill Creek, go to Caring Family Dentistry and ask for Linh! She is a fantastic hygienist—friendly, polite, and extremely thorough. She always makes my cleanings a breeze. Five stars for Linh!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anne Ostrom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIs_fan6zswjWtMzzzrgz-ArowYRNjKgNcbVy7BwETjk8rS4g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so happy I found this office. It is filled with kind, caring professionals that do everything to make you comfortable. I have severe dental anxiety and they did everything they could to make me feel safe and comfortable. I highly recommend Caring Family Drntistry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darryck Schmit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVySuTPMiN9w2LKoddTqff9ccSTPzcw-rxT1lY0A6mFDCxs4lBE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Caring family dentistry has been my dentist for many years now. They're professionalism and great staff keep me coming back. I've recommended them to friends and family without any worries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sandra Villagrana","ProfileP