nd I was genuinely impressed by how kind and welcoming everyone was. Dr. Stinde took the time to listen to my concerns and thoroughly examine a tooth that has been bothering me for almost a year. She explained everything clearly and recommended an Endodontics visit to finally get to the root of the problem.\n\nI really appreciated her professionalism, honesty, and the care she showed throughout the appointment. It’s rare to feel this comfortable during a first dental visit, but the entire team made it easy. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Akana Bbs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItoAlQQOmrTqft-ySFYrBb025qAcvcKBD52JwJyX8Lu3r7Ag=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My husband and I have been going here for years.   Everyone we have encountered is extremely professional and proficient.  They are totally “state of the art” when it comes to dentistry.   And, I trust them.  Even though my husband doesn’t like going to the dentist (probably a hold-over childhood thing), I love going to Crystal Springs Dental - knowing that they are taking excellent care of us and our health!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arezo Murady","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI9HUj7Ryn7c_3gKYNI77AQYlxvnnU13PT6hrUqeLkLKIipcw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Crystal Springs Dental. Victoria was incredibly knowledgeable and took the time to explain each part of the process and the reasons behind it. Unlike other places that rush through the appointment, she pointed out real issues and provided different approaches to address them—without overselling anything. Truly a genuine and professional practice. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Richard Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEY7CpW8zJKtYPO11uTj9PH9XhsZxx0anhThGdQ1-Q9TIQbQ4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are the best.  Jenn is phenomenal and so nice the front office team Michelle and others are fantastic. Many folks hate going to a dentist but they make it fun and comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gordon Beck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWgbY-IAq4WacvXkfDnES7LXzNVXtXODz3qRpmz-bBE_XnAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The people! It always the people! Every person at Crystal Springs is always friendly, helpful, respectful. They each have provided courteous, excellent results. Today I had painless visit with a filling and a fitting for a crown. I've recommended them to my friends and I recommend them to you.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
