ocation and Saturday appointments are sought after here at this practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wes Fujii","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVfYhmQDQiVwrxY-NPErUMlwpTayUbmHq7DR1M_chSzkpC_rA7N=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick to get in and repair after one of my old crowns came off. The office staff is always friendly and professional. The dental assistant was stellar and informative in all aspects of the procedure preparation. All was smooth, and the doctor was caring and efficient. I'm totally thrilled with the visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob Bocskay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmo1JXpbayOtFhzgcv8naPdIhTR4MRkfwToV1aqUi-ylxI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"North Creek Dental has been my dentist for almost 12 years, and even when I have had to switch to other dental providers due to insurance conflicts, they have remembered me, and made me feel like no time has passed! I am grateful for their care, attention to detail with my teeth, and care for my family and I. They will be my dental provider forever!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shellie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXZ1w15HAWOvq-Mk--nZiilhw1diNTW9PsppQfeJSHziw8vw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not a fan of dentist services but the staff at North Creek Dental make it more tolerable. Always smiling and friendly and make my appointments go smoothly. Highly recommend to anyone who is searching for a dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laurie Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRO3oYdUcbGLi7aZ1DQZarAFhZDIrjPxBZqRlGWPqx54-dXR8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadnt been to the dentist since Covid. It was the perfect excuse. I switched to this office and had a really great experience. They are accommodating and understand dental fears.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clinton Shaw","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIidQFT5Bnq-WJw_yB4EnKdJWB1WpDKIYU23Yw-SCBDy8woiVY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Dentist I have had work done at. Very friendly and patient. All the staff are wonderfuI. I kind of always had some dental anxiety but this place  helps take it away. I have been here around 8 times after a long time not going to a dentist. I'm on my way of getting all caught up here soon. If you have feelings of shame over your teeth or high anxiety please just make an appt and just do it for yourself. One day you will look back and be so thankful of yourself.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
