ean afterwards and I have great confidence in my future care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stella Herrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3n0qLIVFPNO5JONs6YBLzK1HdV3wndlhzFe3hptSTNoKErw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Chin was so thorough \u0026 personable and showed genuine concern for my dental issue. She reviewed a plan best suited for my needs.  Her staff were also knowledgeable, professional and caring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christine Moody","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFYcu6p9TDY5oMqwZP1YGpxFCG8wdsJHbhOUhyUGR6_EIjAvNa=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love seeing my dentist at Millcreek dental. She make me feel remembered like we are ol’ friends.\nThat’s how the staff is!!! Love them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathie Torrico","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyQCe2MLNS523vCKFa32dVPNg9PM367Hh1y1wsAuJm522gQg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Chin and her entire staff are wonderful! Very professional and knowledgeable! We feel our dental health is in very capable hands!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dennis Batey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCdZyc0o4ANj9vN18MsplyRaTIWNMr57KeCHb6NkKZnmTa-3Y=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit and I was very pleased with all aspects of my care. Lana, Jen and Dr Chin were very thorough and answered all my questions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bob nale","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI16oJkR6VXASysNNGR8WSq3OKEBwmSUi8A9D_6-qP0IfB8_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m submitting this review to express my heartfelt appreciation for the outstanding customer service I always receive from Dental Hygienist Julia. Her dedication, professionalism, and genuine care for my teeth always leaves a lasting impression on me, and I believe it is essential to acknowledge exceptional service when it is delivered.\n\nFrom the moment I first contacted The Mill Creek Dental Office her exemplary customer service skills were evident. Julia's attentiveness and ability to actively listen to my needs and concerns made me feel valued as a patient. She always shows great patience in addressing all my questions, providing me with detailed and thorough explanations that helps me understand how to care for my teeth.\n\nMoreover, I'm always impressed by Julia's prompt responsiveness. Her willingness to go the extra mile to assist me in finding a solution to my dental care always exceeds my expectations.\n\nFurthermore, Julia's extensive dental hygiene knowledge is evident throughout our communication. She always takes the time to explain the benefits of the various brushing and flossing options available to me.\n\nJulia’s expertise and guidance allows me to make informed decisions that's perfectly suited my dental care needs.\n\nNot only does she advise me on how to care for my teeth effectively, but she also does so in a friendly and positive manner.\n\nJulia’s demeanor throughout our interactions is always warm and welcoming, creating an atmosphere of trust and assurance. Her kindness and professionalism have set a high standard for the Mill Creek Dental Office.\n\nJulia is the best thing that ever happened to the Nikki Chin Mill Creek Dental Office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Gamwell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKxyaAR9j2kvpbpkU2MLOQrq02Hxy4H59zA29TccTiuG4rh_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My last appointment was very productive. I had a long awaited crown fastened to my implant and then a cleaning. Dr. Chin did  the best job and my cleaning was very thorough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vince Domingcil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCJhnRNnXspw1orw16q0N4jlw48GFAORppivbreBR8S5Qqev2G=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful 