.com/a-/ALV-UjVD7MJ5zinD3GexPmVdPiPiTwcmRmr_kfrbo7tg-YQtXoDxIyuVpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience at Mill Creek Dental Health Care has always been excellent. Dr. Habib has been my dentist for many years. She is  friendly, knowledgeable, and trustworthy. I even followed her to this office from her last location. My usual hygienist, Sonya, is also amazing. She is always does an excellent job cleaning my teeth while also being an attentive listener and a joy to talk to. Overall, my experience with all the staff here has always been exceptional and they always try to make the appointment as comfortable and enjoyable as possible. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suzy McCoard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtNTElgmP1i3wXqOi3_DIwWcRVMXkohYydwacylLF41Spb0wOw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff is always kind and helpful. They genuinely seem like they care about you as a person, not just a dental patient. We've been going here for years and have no plans on ever switching!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tara Skelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsNrQCzaNveJ1i_CK8lTDm8P_DR1052pllJFn2u-hW8Pt1WURz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I’ve been going to this office for 8 years and today I encountered the new receptionist. Wow she is the most disrespectful person I’ve come across in the medical field. You’re going to argue with me and say “I’m coming at you” and yelling at you when I never raised my voice I was clearly frustrated about something and she obviously doesn’t have the skill to help resolve the situation! I’m absolutely appalled the way I was treated!! If I didn’t love my dentist and hygienist I’d find another place to go! Everyone there has always been so kind this lady does not fit!!! I’m so angry right now I could spit nails! What happened to customer service!! I would never let my schedulers at my clinic EVER speak to patients like she spoke to me. She’d be terminated immediately. And she wonders why I was upset, she’s the one I spoke to on the phone also horribly rude!! Do better mill creek dental!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jadon Claps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxjrUrS31W7ruZVAqz5ixS5aNdnQ3mEWC7QAfpFQVMiP2evJMZ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sonya did such a great job with my cleaning! Great personality and easy going she did a great job making me feel comfortable during my appointment","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"UW 85","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXE2iLrf8hZxzXG-NzF24WzII-uM8454Fm2S9VKV4wOfyWr6ts=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Maryam is simply the BEST ever. I think she should get a big raise! 😊 Sincerely, very professional yet super nice and personable. Thanks for the making the dentist a fun place to hang out. 👍","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
