to find a dental team that remains this consistent and communicative year after year. Highly recommend!\"","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0toczVKgt_H7okq_lXYtwBJxbppsgdCvyQMMYyo9mrJNU5TI0n8R3jEVJtqWzQAcdxOUmDBNwQoqmX434si14kKMCURE-UqLuCzCeaZVqkDAnL6GKEBHb2FkHISxCvMd0nZK5MXOoJ9sc1=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-6"},{"Name":"Deepthi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKizZccixdlnZdnhrmwZOkmw_uWBtkAs3J9S9kVxVZUPQEraQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a great experience at this dental office! The entire team was professional, friendly, and made me feel comfortable from the moment I walked in. They explained everything clearly and made sure I understood my treatment options. The procedure was smooth, and they really took their time to make sure I was comfortable the whole time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monica Ranjit","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCCincagevpM-LqF44H8fNjaKtk6g9wFDSlKU54zEb3BpmsZ5r=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience with Silvers. The office is clean, the staff is incredibly welcoming, and the care was top-notch. I usually get nervous about the dentist, but they made me feel completely at ease. Highly recommend if you are looking for a professional and gentle dental team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ronald Purvis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuhJFgCcj7n7W5MGUu4A0qErlW7Q-WIDuDL7B4bawXScSI7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a cancer patient with limited mobility, I was deeply grateful for how accommodating and coordinated this dental team was. They worked with my doctor, managed my insurance details, and made the entire visit stress‑free. Outstanding care — a full 10 out of 10.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mehak Dawar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHEEiYaQKhqb4ys7VqpNgXnHCtoEKQHFspq-OEzzz9GC7J=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was treated by Dr. Singh and Dr. Bajwa, and this was honestly one of the worst dental experiences I’ve had so far. I initially went in for a deep cleaning, but was told that I needed some fillings done. After the fillings, I experienced excruciating pain for an entire week.\n\nWhen I returned for a follow-up and explained the pain, I was told, quite casually, that they may have hit the nerve because the filling was very deep, and that I would now need a root canal. As dentists, they should be fully aware of the risks involved and communicate them clearly. The lack of accountability and the casual attitude toward a patient’s pain was extremely disappointing. If the filling was borderline and there was a possibility of nerve involvement, this should have been explained upfront so I could make an informed decision and avoid unnecessary suffering.\n\nIn addition to this, the staff was unprofessional. People frequently walked in during the procedure just to chat, which was very distracting and inappropriate. Overall, I am not happy with my experience and would not recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Govind","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA3fVXJhdbJNGcbNEi1WEXOq2mPKM_fNR3Qj75EN0rPE4J3Es=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great professional service. Dr. Lee and Anjali were respectful and accommodating of my choices as an informed patient. This was by far the most pain-free cleaning I have had in my life. I recommend this clinic for people in the Mill Creek area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rakesh Mangal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW__KHt56_YHuoMFlN2K97dA0vec7a5F4ampqpCD3wjT-otdx8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t recommend Silver Firs Dental enough! From the moment you walk in, you’re greeted by a friendly, professional staff that makes you feel completely at ease and the entire team are exceptional at what they do—thorough, compassionate, and incredibly skilled. They use state-of-the-art technology and ensure that every procedure is as comfortable as possible. They genuinely care about their patients’ well-being and take the time to explain each step of the process. Whether it’s routine cleanings, fillings, or more complex dental work, I’ve always felt I’m in the best hands. If you’re looking for top-notch dental care in a welcoming environment, Silver Firs Dental is truly the best in the business!”","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-jvOisJ2bzltYZTuEBAYL8iecN9pu3p5kbrGffgU9nBs5NpyYqk1Oq_wSGoNkjr8ZHUQDOvyCcUELGYVOur9cub0j-9zCT2H-iOL7D7G1CmGs2dIuVj1gQqBt2tekG1JoEFFI=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-9"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
