rue}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Sumedha Pathak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYO-q220x9pSk_Zn9-mTbalrpBznq1CAyqYZw7Nd23NAQhTnjl=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience here. All staff members, including those at the front desk and the x-ray tech, are welcoming and professional. The office is very clean and offers privacy during procedures. Dr. Rai is knowledgeable, thorough, and took the time to explain everything to me. The dental hygienist, Reji Rajan did a great cleaning without any discomfort, and was also very patient and gentle during the cleaning. Highly recommend this practice to anyone looking for a new dental clinic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samrat Karak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdVTQIFRAhVqlTsKtfnLuL6oNO0655WisjSne2m0e9PqHRCTvK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently started going to Bothell Modern Dentistry, and I’m very happy with my experience! The staff is very friendly and made me feel welcome and at ease. The hygienist, Reji R, was incredibly gentle and caring by frequently checking to see if I was experiencing pain and took the time to explain everything as she went. Thanks to her my deep cleaning experience was painless and a pleasant experience.\n\nDr. Rai was attentive and answered all my questions related to my dental care. I really appreciated that Aimee at the front desk explained the estimated charges and how my treatment plan will work with my insurance before starting my treatment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asha Grinnell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIq-UqRMiN2ekhGXlUemgF3ieGBiS5KGc7aa4BPd4g1aZX6nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a positive experience at Bothell Modern Dentistry, and I can’t say enough good things about Dr. Rai. I’ve always been a bit anxious about dental visits, but she completely put me at ease from the moment I sat in the chair.\n\nDr. Rai is incredibly thorough and attentive. She takes the time to explain everything clearly, answers questions patiently, and makes sure you feel comfortable with your treatment plan. What really stood out to me was her bedside manner — she is calm, kind, and genuinely reassuring, which makes a huge difference if you’re someone who gets nervous about dental care.\n\nInstead of feeling rushed or stressed, I left feeling informed and confident that I’m getting excellent care. It’s rare to find a dentist who combines such professionalism with warmth and compassion.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dental office that is modern, organized, and truly cares about patient comfort, I highly recommend Bothell Modern Dentistry and Dr. Rai. They made a normally stressful experience feel surprisingly positive. 🦷✨","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catalina Salvador","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDz7EJVOOfhkoll7BOOFsmmn8ne5FXLLZxGtVedWchKqZEHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Rai and her team were great! It was easy to schedule. The location and parking very convenient. I had not been to the dentist in many years and they made me feel so comfortable and not at all embarrassed. Dr. Rai had a very professional but ready going personality that makes you feel at ease. Everything was explained to me in detail, treatment and financial aspects. My actual treatment was comfortable, quick and painless. I appreciate the care given to me by the whole team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alex Tan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUYAMv-3PBLqNB4zhN5bibr-HWufqIBeau6XtgWjQgjAEgyj31vw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff, clean facilities, excellent care. At the front desk, Shay is friendly and is very effective at her job. Dr. Rai was professional, informative, and exhibited a high level of care. Reji (hygienist) skillfully performed a deep cleaning with such care that I felt no pain. She was very calm, transparent, and professional. This is a top notch group that has earned my respect.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anu Bush","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIDsbsm-4uIglxlzi1hCFiH6lNYqsorxshPfqyrwPWXVGokA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in as a new patient for myself and two kids and my experience has been lovely! Everyone is so nice and helpful and the process from x rays to deep cleaning was very informative. The hygienist Reji was very understanding about the discomfort of deep cleaning and super helpful about recommendations for after care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVx6iXho6MxR-xuXiS1yThTyUg_LKYtu6G1Y9qbHeagfPsMigpVLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentistry is really nice and thorough! I moved here from the Bellevue Modern Dentistry and the quality of service is still very good.\nThey’re very clear and transparent about what you are getting for the appointment and the people are very nice. Dr. Rai explained everything even medically so I knew what was going on. They reviewed insurance with me too before the service just to double check with me which I appreciate.\nShana also helped out with the x rays and it didn’t hurt at all (the mouthpieces)! Usually at other dentistries it hurts.\nAll together, I appreciate the kind transparent team and the quality care (it didn’t hurt).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"inga africa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxKMPTJdRSRDtEbQpxML5hs8gXNCc51-KoySJGa5TPvsV-SpI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was looking for a new dentist and had such a pleasant first experience here. The staff is incredibly friendly, made me feel comfortable from the moment I walked in, and were very accommodating when it came to payment options. They are also very thorough, which really put me at ease. Because of how positive my first visit was, I’ve continued my treatments with them and couldn’t be happier. I highly recommend this office to anyone looking for a caring and professional dental team.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
