ental singlehandedly cured my fear of the dentist. I had previously had a pretty terrible experience at a dentist, which caused intense anxiety regarding the dentist. From my first visit, they created an environment that was focused on kindness, healing, and support. I was incredibly anxious but the staff went above and beyond to help me. The next time I came in, mulitple staff members came over to tell me they were proud of me and that they were so glad I was there. They validated my fears, while working to help me feel calm. Now, every time I have an appointment, I get excited about going to the dentist.\n\nOne thing that also stands out to me is that for one appointment they were running slightly behind, which was no problem at all. I received a handwritten note in the mail apologizing for the delay. I was totally fine waiting, but it goes to show how much they care about their patients.\n\nI could not be more thankful for Beardslee Dental  and all they have done to help restore my confidence. Thank you all at Beardslee Dental :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Transducer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvQg5A4x643cc9r7c9SpI_YvSEM6nmQdFWFRNcz7x9wRn8DQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Beardslee Dental. Dr. Kramarevsky fixed a chipped tooth for me and did an outstanding job! The repair looks completely natural, and the whole process was smooth and painless. She took the time to explain what was happening and made sure I was comfortable the entire visit. The staff was friendly, the office felt welcoming, and I left feeling very happy with the care I received. Highly recommend Dr. Kramarevsky and the Beardslee Dental team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"C.S.W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTAG2wK3KAuPRD4lULwTa7uQqZYuxRuYBqdzjhgO56VEEQp7fl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in for myself and two kids, 7 and 9. The staff was wonderful, kind and attentive, and it felt very warm and welcoming. Will definitely be making our regular appointments here after our initial ones went so well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"McKenzie Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXnqApSizRvLmlcFza6-FcGGbJlULf4OCEwmi6tURO1-khnTaZD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office has restored my trust in dentists! From Suzi who took my initial pictures and X-rays, to Dr. Carmody who discussed the X-rays and treatment plan, to Emma who did the most gentle and thorough cleaning. THANK YOU! It had been about 5 years since my last cleaning and I’ve had horrible dental experiences before, so I’ve just stayed away from the dentist. Now I’m comfortable coming back regularly because I know I’ll be well taken care of.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fish","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmHscYg2Ics-A20hoFosP7xO83lYXnz5Jb5r4NAkno9F4qdRio=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beardslee Dental has truly excellent bedside manner. I got care from multiple people, and they were all kind, considerate, and not preachy. They helped me schedule some urgent care very quickly. Pain management was done carefully and effectively.  Especially if you have anxiety about going to the dentist, I highly recommend Beadslee Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Edwards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUmB4PVAYkWrQIbAmmTUTXIHq_nY-rm82cYGn1w_d3cdcpqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Beardslee Dental for about 5 years now and will continue for years to come! I would highly recommend Beardslee Dental to anyone searching for a new dentist. They are careful and precise when operating on me and I never dread dentist appointments because I have confidence in Dr. Carmody and the dental hygienists that work for her. I know that I am going to have a great experience and my teeth will be cared for properly. Furthermore, Dr. Carmody is an expert in her field. She not only tells you what’s going on, but she educates you with the “why” things are the way that they are. The dental hygienists are highly skilled at what they do and they are very careful when avoiding pains and sensitivities during the teeth cleaning. The office is very well kept and clean, and everyone is friendly and respectful making the whole experience enjoyable. Thank you Beardslee Dental for making visits to the dentist easy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWCFIEkRyaeN_EpAZnCmM85WvdRLAwnS4-Lb0jVYbyqORcbFVk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had the best cleaning ever - removed a lot of coffee stains.  I highly recommend Beardslee Dental for the more complicated crowns/fillings, etc.  Dr. Carmody restructured my tooth under a crown and did an amazing job.  For everyday check ups you can get away with an okay dentist, but when something goes wrong you'll want experienced and confident professionals.  Dr. Carmody is a great choice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mic A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoa780uHM-445ef1_SXHL7m51_voKUgoiHlRK9GR7LwfGwwZY4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have a lot of dental anxiety and Dr. Carmody \u0026 staff listened respectfully \u0026 more importantly took their cues from me. If I felt uncomfortable or verging on panic, we had a signal \u0026 they immediately stopped \u0026 allowed me time to compose. They explained every step, and what they were about to do. I felt very comfortable, with their compassion \u0026 professionalism. I had a broken molar \u0026 needed a crown and they explained all options and allowed me choices. They were very upfront with costs \u0026 those costs did not change. I can't recommend them enough.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
