d":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Randy Koch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLMSwRkHTi3_eLiv83iTeZy9TshdoES0A_OtXoci1MSToRfBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife has been seeing Dr. Stayner since he started his practice, and his father since the early 70's! (She even babysat him back then).\nI've been seeing him since around 2018.\nHe is a great Dentist and a great person.\nHis staff is terrific as well.\nWe both only have great things to say about everyone there!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracee Hayes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjzosvYJS3y8n4lGQeU5BlRVxosdmFP0k4lUKG9OXJI0C4Mw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly the best dental experience I've probably ever had in my life. It's the first experience with a dentist office where I have felt seen and cared for and genuinely look forward to my next appointment!\n\nThank you so much for today!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lexi A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOr14maZpEha5fNldX3Ss1e_7BswsET8Yh-qCAr2_jseBUlyjV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was absolutely terrified to get my rotting tooth pulled out. I was so afraid that I waited until I could not take the pain anymore and I was maxed out on anti-inflammatory pain/over-the-counter meds Plus Orajel plus salt rinses. plus fresh garlic, waiting 5 to 10 minutes and then swallowing it for the antibacterial effects. Plus coconut oil +clove oil. They got me in same day. There was no way I was going to make it to an actual scheduled appt.  Dr. Sarhangi (I think that’s how you spell it) was very kind and understanding and made the process seamless. He didn’t push any decisions onto me but was informative about outcomes, costs, etc.  The young woman who helped out (probably the main instigator for my seamless experience) with the procedure and set up and all that was also very kind, and she had an uplifting ease about her that was contagious and radiated the room, it even shined through my crippling anxiety. As the tooth was extracted she was there to give positive affirmation and support and it really helped my comfort levels in the moment. I hope this helps ease the minds of others so they don’t wait as long as I did.\n\n10/10 would get my tooth pulled out here again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zjhtK-C6tmK0s31q5QcWCTPpQ6CW94tZI4P5Y7fbYHQZeItDhOuucvTM8Tfpw6DV93NZ7m7uEJdKLOA52orn6CuJMzEzMs8r9blH6LfnyJJnqhPWbFHAjV7O_vn-qK_yQqRxN1an2u2H8=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Megan Law","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK_oyO_Kn5jzjA2NmxugpbLnIlZuACPlBVbo7VpVjKa-1rgUM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Office staff is amazing and extremely helpful and I have seen one other dentist but the main one I have been seeing isn’t very friendly. I have severe dental anxiety and every time I go I always feel anxious and ashamed if I need work done and the dentist could really work on his delivery of the bad news. I am only giving 3 stars because of the office staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Bollinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoCSsTpR41-FOj9qCZDfg0LpfdOSbepZT-ngqZ59UisYicK7RtnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been to many family dentistry clinics across the West coast, finally found one I will come back to.\nTheir customer service was amazing, I felt very comfortable.\nFrom the front desk to the dentist I encountered professionalism the entire process.\nThank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Denni Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9FdIdf5qtTa6jY_8cKG547InpQDFDLH7nTGpMq3vCh3oAYw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was excellent friendly and informative. Doctor Pratt always does excellent work with a cheerful spirit. I highly recommend them. I saw the bad review. I'm sorry you didn't insist on the n... and you had anxiety and cried, I think it would of been with any dentist but Again my sympathy. Dental work IS Very Hard for some people.  Other dentists in the past leave a gap and food Has to Be glossed out. Again 5 🌟 s.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Irene Henninger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2utxVgirPfeKU6DxexovYrVZDRX5yllvCBTIptz1pNsiyZxSe=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The hygienist Ashley was super friendly and helpful. She thoroughly explained everything to me and answered all my questions. Dr Pratt also did a good job of explaining his concerns and asking if I had any more questions. The cleaning etc all went great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tawna Wilsey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVxGqRTqprDN8EyCxhH0q2M6CDunO8Q8fGUSYzymNwHtRSsNv4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family has gone to Monroe Family Dentistry since 2006.  Great dental hygienists, dentists (We see Dr Pratt).  We now live an hour’s drive away and we still travel back since we like this clinic so much.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
