Smiles for 5+ years and have had nothing but positive experiences. Dr. Wu, Kira, and the entire front office staff are amazing — extremely professional, warm, and always make you feel welcome.\n\nBeyond their personalities, I trust them to do excellent work, whether it’s a routine cleaning or replacing a crown. Dr. Wu is incredibly knowledgeable and takes the time to explain everything thoroughly. He’s even drawn a picture or two to help me better understand what’s going on with my teeth.\n\nTheir pricing is fair, they are never pushy, and I’m very grateful I found them when I moved to Washington. Thanks team for taking care of my teeth (and encouraging me to do so at home too) ✨🦷🪥","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rosalind Levene","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVowVyCv97BXXNXpHBOiDA7jCMyLvJQR1R0rzHIC7rLA4GPuJJV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is friendly, professional and very knowledgeable    They answer every question .\nI have never experienced a doctor that really understood my problems as Dr Wu did\nHe explained to me step by step everything I needed.  Also Dr. Wu was interested in all my past health issues and how that influence with my deteriorating bones and tooth.\nI felt wonderful at the dentist office and that is not easy  for me to do!\nGreat doctor and great staff members.\nVery good experience!  A+","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monir Imamverdi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfRpbf-d4MsqDPTkVDPXHWHRKxf1mUfurhI2arvUGVbYQy-nFR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Dr. Wu is certainly very knowledgeable and enjoys taking his time to explain various dental related topics to you. However, when it comes to your dental health, Dr. Wu is guilty of what causes many so people to turn away from dentists, and that is shamelessly pushing unnecessary treatments on you.\n\nHe seems more interested in filling up his book and charging your insurance than listening to you and tending to your needs.\n\nHe pushed me on three separate occasions to get my wisdom teeth removed despite them being in perfectly healthy shape. The reason? Maybe, perhaps, one day in the future they will get cavities and it's just easier to get rid of them than to maintain them. I even asked the assistant, albeit somewhat jokingly, to tell the doctor I'm keeping my wisdom teeth before he sees me. But he didn't care, he pushed me anyway.\n\nAt the very end of my exam, he scheduled me for 5 fillings with very vague reasonsand rushed out of the room. His best one was that he felt something soft with tool despite the xray came back clean. It was, perhaps unsurprisngly, one of my wisdom teeth. His poor assistant had to sit back and awkwardly explain things to me as I was left genuinely befuddled. A few days later, seeing a hygenist for a routine cleaning, she was looking at my file and telling me that 3 of the 5 were \"very optional\".\n\nI have the highest and utmost respect for the assistants and the hygenists who work at Signature Smiles. They are extremely professional and beyond kind. It's a shame that Dr. Wu spends most of his mental energy on salesmanship and pushing needless treatments rather than focusing on the patient experience and establishing trust. Someone tell him he's not Alex Hormozi and that he doesn't need to hustle every person that steps into his practice like he's running some online course business. This is a medical establishment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monica Novotny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUplMZgP-nOyWAB7GHx2HiUSCAiPgLbW2ocCNyVkeJ_X9cUvUU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Signature Smiles for at least 10 years now. I've always had a good experience, even for those \"unpleasant\" procedures.  The atmosphere is nice and comfortable without being pretentious. The staff always feels knowledgeable and helpful as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiny Orchestral Moments","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpB6E14blyri7-Yef2b2rwnP5-klisyBKsoFN5MvlUnSHfgG8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Wu and his staff are great! They are knowledgeable professional. Dr. Wu is so skilled at filling tough cavities that I didn't need to get three crowns.   Very talented.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Callahan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLThY-QwtSSmB8pB-3uh8ncXrw03Yvs6VIKrR9vSY5zqBZzPg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist I’ve had ever. So kind, caring and conservative.\nDr Wu, Dr Dowd, Corie and Leslie are so genuine and kind. Great office and location","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ann Lamb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqOP3wVUHzsl9ggMNkTLf6tUrWDCN4oYBCMlRgqQFMW5Vg5w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was in and out quickly as I had to get to work. They were very thorough and fixed the problem. Highly recommend Dr Wu and his excellent team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judith Compton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAnIO8GWZ26G1blB3nFBr0VbM1E3m51R451Ulxjzy6fIS7Yw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going here for years. They’re always kind, accommodating, and efficient. I feel they truly only recommend what’s needed. I trust everyone 100%.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
