"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Toon Aom Seattle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwifz9QwODt2bzl5Ir617G44DbKa7eEguBeBCqGamGtAOeiPgwjQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a dental emergency and needed to be seen the very next day. 8 to 8 Dental took our case right away, and we are extremely grateful to have a clinic we can truly trust. The staff are professional, friendly, and caring.\n\nDr. Thongin is wonderful—he recommends what’s truly important and never tries to have us spend money unnecessarily. We appreciate his honesty and expertise.\n\nWe can’t recommend 8 to 8 Dental enough. They are fantastic!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yong Tsai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVW9nFItooo8Dg66PPMZk5WpHv3DqXlZQUDD6m3-v5_I7ZTbZgK0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I could not said enough good things about 8 to 8 Dental and especially how skilled and caring is Doctor Thongin on my dental care and recent implant of my molar  experience. On 8 to 8 admin.  system  ,appointments are promptly reminded and all billings are accurate and no issues and smooth . My implant experience was top notch with excellent results and patience and  patient care and no pain philosophy are the cornerstones of Doctor Thongin practice. Recommend all your friends  here to 8 to 8 dental , you will be cared for and cost is very competitive also","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy Stoose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUg7Fpd1Rltm0VZIf8cNpd3NkyZBBsHk_XLrM_lLhQhojXbrTf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Isaac and Dr. Bai are always amazing!! My mother is older and has dementia, so Isaac's nature is always a great calming factor for her. He is so patient and kind that it makes me not stress when I have to take her for her appointments. If any of you have older parents, I definitely recommend asking for Isaac to assist/hygienist. Doctor Bai is always so professional and guides us in the right direction with our care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ritthi Thirajitto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-8zej1LTYccN2AkfXif_rV3VXJp6l8q3dwTNb1-lkYV7uWVU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Thongin is a skillful and thoughtful dentist.  He cares about patients and what would be best for the condition. He always spent time explaining the problems before gave the best solution to me. The work he has done  lasted a pong time. He really does care about his works and patients altogether. Thank you for being so sincere and gentle to me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shawn Cha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYInf2G-V4jZexYsyGGPpSJd1RwqNLIY4V_JcYV4AQaP_Swjwy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here after a couple years of not visiting the dentist and it was amazing. From the warm welcoming Lobby to the Front Staff to the Doctors and Assistants it was an amazing experience. I would insist on getting your treatment and dental care done here. Professional and educational only seeking the best for you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thaksaporn De May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYDowkZOkDT3rc8rlVoZWWrmpcl-p8bX8MtepUPba4CUSdTBgyOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic dentist! Very quick to make an appointment, very thorough, and very professional. The whole team is friendly and the clinic is spotless. I have been seeing Dr. Thongin more than 20 years. High recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Schein","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWk_jjCxz_LGZqLb8YiBKqX1cuJ7USRxNAN1B52N0X524KU1FRK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming here for many years, and the level of care has always been excellent. The whole team is professional, friendly, and thorough. I’ve always felt that the value for the quality of work and attention to detail is outstanding. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a trustworthy dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Polina Ryjov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3xcM4PCVs7H1x9obwY6VuubeGgDxJSc1f5nxRhZxXUOiiMub-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this place! The front desk lady, Tira? Tina? Tiana? Not sure her name but she was fantastic, and very helpful. Always feels very welcome when coming in.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
