vations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"104731187877717075140","name":"Sunshine Dental Care (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104731187877717075140"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Canyon Park","street":"22010 17th Ave SE","city":"Bothell","postal_code":"98021","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Language assistance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"JUDY BAI","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULM8Iim72tE8kg-Xn7jYCusxleSR9e4kWfCi5QCOs9dtpuy_cO=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this dental clinic. The entire team is extremely professional and welcoming. The clinic is always clean and well-organized, which made me feel comfortable right away.\n\nDr. Gregory Wang ’s skills are truly excellent. He provides perfect treatment with great attention to detail. What I appreciate most is how he treats patients with respect and makes them feel relaxed and comfortable throughout the entire visit.\n\nThey don’t just focus on treatment — they also give helpful advice and great ideas, especially for kids, to maintain good dental habits. That extra care and guidance really make a difference.\n\nI highly recommend this clinic to anyone looking for professional, high-quality dental care in Bothell area.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dane Herforth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKH-meNDKzRYRFrImYva92oIYm0TL4kqQqzf_OeLiWZkpLDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a new patient who hadn't seen a dentist in 5+ years, I was feeling a little anxious on the day of my exam and cleaning. All of that melted away as soon as I began meeting the team at Sunshine Dental Care. Everyone was super friendly and warm. Dr. Wang has a kind, laid-back, and down-to-earth demeanor. He was honest and communicative, and very present with me during my appointment. I highly recommend Sunshine Dental Care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Salina Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXw5MmsdGsxUDogyerfiqB3iWHxw5kD7PcvBajqBd7eNmfpphuG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Gregory Wang is an amazing dentist, very patient, detail-oriented, and always remembers my preferences. He truly goes above and beyond to accommodate my schedule and even fit me in on one of his off days with the help of his wife, Sherry, so I wouldn’t miss my cleaning. They are a lovely couple who genuinely care about their patients. My mom, my husband, and I all see Dr. Wang and will continue to do so!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Andrea Chong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4daJp8jSA_yaVhtjDm_EMrXptFVwfbJB1kM0OKApuP8FlXA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had wonderful experiences with Dr. Wang and his team. He is exceptionally thorough and gentle, as well as taking the time to make sure I’m comfortable throughout every procedure. Dr. Wang is also very patient in explaining my dental health and educating me on the proper way to clean my teeth, which I really appreciate. The staff is friendly, and very accommodating with scheduling. I feel welcomed and well cared for during every visits.\n\nI highly recommend this dental clinic if you are in the Bothell area!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"NealS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbRp685B0p1rsrQERihF_1HjjCrcE1BpArhrYCxwx6pJbqxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience here as a new patient! Dr. Wang, Zoey, and Jenny were all incredibly friendly and professional, and it was clear they truly prioritize patient care. It didn’t feel like a place only focused on maximizing insurance benefits—just genuine, thoughtful treatment and attention.\n\nDr. Wang was especially kind and patient—he checked in with me throughout the entire exam to make sure I was comfortable and then spent time afterward clearly explaining everything. I left with a much better understanding of my dental health and a treatment plan that was tailored to what I need right now versus what can be monitored over time.\n\nOverall, it was a wonderful visit. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lisa yan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtvJTtsBqFm-68iaQUEUTDAJd6Ev1dOnDCXqTAss1h4ZLL2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been seeing Dr. Wang at Sunshine Dental Care for years, and I couldn’t be happier. They truly care about their patients—always take time to explain everything and make sure I’m comfortable. The staff is warm and welcoming, and the office feels calm and clean. Highly recommend to anyone who wants a dentist who genuinely cares.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Skyler Tsai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkyZ90II-4F6lx_-N8RCgKFDhTx3tBOy41f_XGAcfHTw3YNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone at this clinic is wonderful. Extremely understanding with rescheduling and staff created a very welcoming environment. I'm inspired by Dr. Wang's passion for his work and care for his patients. Most dentists provide great care, but Dr. Wang educates you about your health— better than any other dentist I've ever seen. Despite the distance from my home, I always look forward to coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anderson Quach","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXICe9o2l-3eXCBkJVNqekec2uYztQ_v-gxdmwpgy8OqvtkkeYv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Get my dental work done by Dr. Gregory Wang. Everybody at the clinic from front desk, the dental assistants, and the doctor himself is nice, helpful and polite. Even on simple cleaning appointments, they put in the full effort to really clean everything out instead of doing a lazy job like other dental offices I've been in.\n\nI really like that they're informative about my visit as well, I know it takes time for them to answer questions or explain how everything is going with my teeth. After getting fillings, he'll show me before and after images and explain what was done. He'll recommend brands/brushing techniques not because he's trying to sell things, but tells me the reasoning behind why he trusts some brands or recommends different products so I'm not blind in buying things like new electric toothbrushes.\n\nThe way he provides his care is preventative, it shows he genuinely cares about the dental treatment he gives rather than patients coming back in for expensive procedures. I've never felt like I was rushed out, and would love to see his clinic successfully grow so I can continue getting the same genuine care over the years. Thank you, Sunshine Dental!\n\nMerry Christmas/Happy Holidays!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
