enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Free street parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jeffery Agyekum Adjei","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWHznerpdt467pu4ILTTcDPo3ZQfITCBd-Db3jJZqnJOkC9L-jItQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an exceptional first time experience at Ideal Dental this morning! The office is equipped with state-of-the-art technology, and the staff were friendly, professional, and welcoming. The facility itself was new and spotless, creating a comfortable atmosphere from the start.\n\nThe X-ray process was quick and efficient, and what really impressed me was the detailed 3D imaging they provided. The dentist took the time to walk me through the scans, explaining everything clearly and highlighting both the positives and areas for improvement. Their approach made me feel informed and at ease.\n\nI highly recommend Ideal Dental to anyone looking for a modern, patient-focused dental experience. The team exceeded my expectations, and I'm definitely going back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25B_Wf_Z06VTZMJi78xdDcKSm2fxLbq2yGgAauwHkWABthGlkHH4mj2XtrPT4cYv_y67_0QIx88YfFiAFW2f6kRMxybbYbiLNqqj182LksgGNqGaYFOcnIWLJv4-z3DOqqfqCiif8RIhhI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1iqwXh4SxwtbRbZf7_3ikM7pAYS3VlDF9Gvl43MBhlzKQGYRwtirxaFjDBqlDaH6UKwZSibL1aQ04KQf5STgU905EnsRz3ytlHptq9odhI5rATEkkzu2q5gsf5NhPGS5JcqbZkLVP-OCqi=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-14"},{"Name":"Galyna Bagdasarov","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGaJbt5KchuF6umbqoky-ah0KN7fwLG6sOoi-1D0ppacR60Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience with my dental exam and cleaning at Ideal Dental Lynnwood today! I used to have a dental office in the past which I absolutely loved. But unfortunately I had no longer my dental insurance and while they offered a dental plan which worked for me, they stopped carrying it and I was looking for a different dental practice that would not only satisfy my dental needs but also provide affordable prices for someone without dental insurance. I had to call a lot of dental offices and to my overwhelming knowledge the prices varied so much and no one offered any dental plans. Ideal Dental instantly got my attention on google and when I called I scheduled my appointment right away. My experience did not disappoint. Friendly, professional, attentive staff, got all my questions answered. Dr. Kim was very knowledgeable and provided me with the information I needed. I was having a rough morning and my dental experience uplifted my spirits and put a smile back on my face which is something that you don’t hear often about dental experiences. So it’s a great dental place for someone without dental insurance since they offer various dental plans. And also very stylish, innovative, clean place with friendly, caring and attentive staff. Hope it will keep providing great experience at affordable prices!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Piilani Chandler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJl1qIktTmKuJx7Dy2hzGzOtQBu3EQXWtV0MpcfzP09VNWFWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Ideal Dental! The entire team was welcoming, professional, and genuinely cared about my comfort from start to finish.The office itself was spotless, modern, and equipped with the latest technology, which made the visit feel efficient and stress-free. .  Overall, Ideal Dental delivers professional, compassionate care, and I feel confident coming back for all my future dental needs. also if you don’t have dental insurance, they offer plans in house. I was able to purchase a one year plan for two free cleanings, two free exams and 20% to 75% off of Other dental procedures.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Magi Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAFR2RRsJnL2J8ENnBX_gHAPQSmDtqkjC3H2DR_W_40NshAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"6 months after my initial appointment in July, where I paid in full before leaving and had absolutely no outstanding balance, I was charged an additional adjustment fee with no explanation or reasoning - feels dishonest. When calling for an explanation, I was unable to reach anyone who could explain what it was and was told I would receive a call back.\n\nDuring my initial exam, everyone was pleasant and nice, however, they told me I had one cavity and quoted me the cost, wanting me to come in as soon as possible to get it fixed. Instead, I went for a second opinion at another dentist, where I was told I had absolutely zero cavities. Since sometimes people can make mistakes, I didn’t want to leave a negative review, but after seeing their lack of communication and seemingly dishonest billing practices on top of that, I wanted to share my experience. It feels like this dentist is out to make as much money as possible and is not truly looking out for the patient or patient experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ronald Rucker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLM86nYMx6n0w4xmkmI2gdwg172s9NVFBdyk2w_637fZbd8bx-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at Ideal Dental, which is weird to say for a dentist appointment. Melina at the front was super welcoming and friendly and made good conversation while checking in. Alexandria did a fantastic job with making my scans, cleaning and X-rays quick and efficient. Dr Kim clearly takes pride in his work and went the extra mile for me by fitting me in the same day to replace some old fillings. He has a very steady hand and clearly a lot of experience in dentistry. I felt cared for here and recommend this dentist office to anyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rich Hernández","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXgGRlifojRg9FqcV09lDhyUlPtPhtRZqmXbTWluospDviglHePw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best dentist visit I have had in a very long time at Ideal Dental.\n\nMalina at the front desk sets the tone the moment you walk in. Her unreasonable hospitality is real. She is welcoming, calm, and genuinely kind. You feel taken care of right away.\n\nAlexandra was gentle and thoughtful in getting me ready for my visit with Dr. Kim. She explained what she was doing and made the whole process easy and comfortable.\n\nDr. Kim was thorough, informative, and efficient. No rushing. No confusion. Clear explanations and solid care.\n\nThis is how a dental visit should feel. I highly recommend Ideal Dental Lynnwood.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jordan taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ88la1iUoQxdnuvYK1aSnzh1rpqvFAF7PDk9JyqXcCJ_jU5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been a patient at Ideal Dental for well over a year now - until recent when all care over my treatment plan for my teeth came to a hault when the new “Dentist” came into replace the last amazing Lady they had running this location. From the very first appointment he paused my treatment to get me rescanned and do a new approach with my treatment, even though the previous Dr here just did that exact thing 2 weeks prior. He did not even examine me himself, it was an assistant who also, I had never seen before. After about 4 months of this back and forth, he had shaven my teeth, completely stopped my invisalign treatment and sent me on my way with no trays to leave with, he held onto them. I still have “buttons” on my teeth now MONTHS later. Never once reached out to me to even attempt to continue my treatment, nothing. Absolute silence. This location has done nothing but fail me since he has taken over. Seems to be the common consensus after reading some other posts from previous patients that has also chosen to leave and pay yet again all the money in the world to go to someone else and restart something that he never should’ve stopped or even interrupted. Absolute ZERO star rating. I would NEVER recommend this location or this Dr to anyone. I have had to spend over 2 grand on botox for my jaw at this point because of how much pain this “man” has left me in. Terrible. Shut it down. Complete money grab. They do not care about you, your comfortability, or the treatments you’re paying for. They do not even attempt to make it go smoothly or correct. Just constant unnecessary changes and haults. This process here will haunt me forever. Leaving someone with their smile absolutely wrecked does something to a person and they don’t even realize any of it. They treat you less than human. Do NOT waste your time here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ibra hero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX4uYGd21mO1ek1EEBbFDW9DT2jpMb6DCqjTh871mn31BAj9yu6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a very disappointing experience at this dental clinic. They seemed to look for ways to charge extra beyond what was initially discussed. The teeth cleaning was poorly done and felt rushed. On top of that, I wasted a lot of time waiting, as the doctor kept leaving to deal with other patients and coming back intermittently. Overall, it felt unprofessional and not respectful of my time. I would not recommend this clinic based on my experience for the first time.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
