tal office. There are not enough good things to say about Bothell Family Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica McGee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX0oPaegT3oguYhVwD-yx2RiQRR8rcDerK8HR5j9BNBYe2IvLjfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Hwang is a wonderful dentist, kind, calm, understanding and friendly. His staff is just as wonderful and helpful. I have never had a bad experience here, I highly recommend this dental office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Asya Ogannisyan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCyOeiwNDRFCmnXu4UrGPmWvNbt0dl53gamLRW5ysfUMU0KA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was here and the doctor professionally pulled out my wisdom tooth. I really liked how he worked professionally.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brian Tsai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUelfNv3o07XQEjWCG0Y6MN0-6o_vbK23XIkxLiugyAOfqkg20i=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had two separate dental emergencies and each time they accommodated me in their already busy schedule and took great care of me.  They made the stressful situation a breeze to deal with. Dr. Hwang, Michell, Sara and everyone at the office are warm, caring, and friendly, highly recommend it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"min xie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLxDX6ScTztX1BP2trAC8Y-SzCt7azo4RMD6pXFAABMnscYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best dental service I have experienced so far. Receptionist is so friendly and patient. She explained all the detailed process and billing information. Doctor Chiang is really knowledgeable and explain the treatment details with you patiently. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Louie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXsfvaWbDepBYjdezgkvsyofzqDZ-oBTNvHGdnCNGrdxV1cR1yp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Hwang is a great dentist and utilizes newer technology compared to other dentists I’ve been to. He has a gentle touch and does a thorough job. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lovely Beth Ellington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJY4L4Ra_D5CVZTJk7Lm_TYFGqdpyuAkOTW84r74bpPzUEjkw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place, it makes you feel like you are part of their Family. Dr. Hwang is such an amazing dentist, very caring and he makes time for every patient. Kudos to everyone! I would highly recommend this place.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darby Ash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLv1y1a7gc9qleLVg79QPCksPgn43d2bbzT8zm7knB-aa8tYfB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I hadn't gone to a Dentist in 4 years, so was expecting a new Dentist to give me a list of \"need to haves\" which is what has happened in the past. I had an exam and cleaning, was told that everything looked good. This was a pleasant surprise because I have had pits in my teeth since teen years, the the dentist I grew up with said they were genetic and not to get talked in to filling them - MANY dentists has tried to get me to fill them. This dentist also said they were genetic, so unless he sees a change over time, the pits shouldn't be messed with. SO, 5 stars for a dentist that is conservative and caring - will be sending my whole family.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
