,{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Tim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXhz69nP6t6hKUkOKKcfXriwPdA60d9xFVozjMwnE6h1Wpcic=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at Mukilteo Dental Center. The entire staff is friendly, professional, and welcoming, but I especially want to recognize Patricia. She is incredibly kind, caring, and attentive. She constantly checked to make sure I was comfortable and doing okay, and she made me feel completely at ease even though it had been a very long time since my last dental visit.\n\nPatricia is hands down the best dental hygienist I’ve ever had. Her positive attitude and genuine care for her patients really stand out. I highly recommend Mukilteo Dental Center to anyone looking for a great dental office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bella Arens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgaJNk2xBqQhDtU0DHHCPAdRR77JvEpe2lmMtHq6jKKHiljT8l_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Pham and her entire team are truly the best of the best. As a dental professional, I've had the privilege of working with the MDC team more than once, and you won't find a kinder, more knowledgeable, more caring, and more fun-loving group of people anywhere. And you won't believe how beautiful, modern, and technology savvy this place is. If you're looking for a fantastic, skilled, and trustworthy dental office, look no further.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lBNB7yh2bJsRgD10V2QlORIwndApjh2TBMeiMrsjhYXeLLmdNwP6jrgitRueOGtm1eItbJlrt1QVUiOI98I0JkH3EUTB3vhnfQOifTKLvjuXZUVSymdTWD8_pOdkiBmW2D5kC8B_DLW1b=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1qGyGeiTbdl-4ghsfG333r8V39Om5pQRQceAJ4ZZCuuhYXwfhmSgG9DeeFtKYtUUIGDTv4RuRCbzygK4H5T9c5rN_UI_4szdSHrMsAnMOr8jyjZQxpL0ZxR0P1y01eWTRudFYP8iOEmt9E=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-9"},{"Name":"Alanna Woodward","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWlV9vPiQg7O60kZQWcktbaMBXEEr56Z6UV_BY1v9-mrz0Dxv0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is so great. Every single person I’ve interacted with has been beyond kind. I’ve gone to so many different dentists across multiple states and have never experienced such gentle dentistry. Dr. Morris is so kind and patient and welcoming. The dental tech who worked on me before Dr Morris, Maria, was THE most gentle flosser I’ve ever had. She was so gentle and careful with my teeth/gums and was so cautious not to bother a painful spot where I bit my lip prior to the visit. If you have any fear or trepidations about dental work, this place and these techs are absolutely the place for you. If you want to get dental work done by some of the loveliest and kindest people, this is also the place for you. Also have to say I LOVE their cute photo montages they play in the lobby.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"danielle malig (ohdangdanii)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgqN5RYtJtuRQmmHMDO0jzRbKS8Fg1roZFo1VcEGHgacFRL_3F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been a client of MDC since moving to Washington state. Their office used to be a much smaller, near Mukilteo beach and they have expanded so much since then!\n\nWhat hasn’t changed is their emphasis on hospitality, information, and quality. Tracie did my cleaning today, and WOW was it impressive! Seriously the best I’ve had in— probably my lifetime? She was gentle, detailed, and efficient. Tracie took the time to explain the long-term effects of my permanent retainer and my options for continuing to have it or deciding to swap it for a more traditional retainer option.\n\nAs someone who takes oral care very seriously, I am very appreciative of a good quality cleaning and the information that I need to make informed decisions about my longer term oral health.\n\nThank you Tracie and Dr. Pham— you guys are the best in the biz. Your whole team deserves to know that they are rockstars at what they do! I will be a FOREVER patient. 🦷❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chase Pelletier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWef4okbq34qFrBOamFWRvFLn4rGRsQUs3w-JUS4L-xuKJ_qaN=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been coming to this practice for at least, oh gosh, has it been 10 years now?? We live over an hour away for the last few and still make the drive. They are that good. The care, the professionalism, the kindness, the positivity, I could go on. No really, I can. When you find care like this, you just don't let it go, they really do take care of you, oh and your smile does more than sparkle, it lingers after you leave. ✨️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcie Costello","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkTDKsCk-PYshkQMZ5QBLHdKUfdKahcJFdTjqtClZpnPsRWedOJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best experience at MDC yet! My dental hygienist was fantastic. I can’t remember her name, but when I was leaving I tried to request her for my next appointment and they said she would be leaving on maternity leave soon. She was the best hygienist I’ve ever had. She was gentle and thorough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taryn Salter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVigJrmbgVeIrXl97KWzcVjmMnD8Ki7ezrScPcC6YDM3E5kJxyI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Mukilteo Dental Center for a while now, and every visit exceeds my expectations. The staff is incredibly friendly, professional, and always makes me feel comfortable. There’s a smile every where you look…. to the left and the right :). ALL of the Doctors are skilled, gentle, and take the time to explain procedures clearly. The office is clean, modern, and equipped with the latest technology. I truly appreciate the care and attention to detail they provide. This place makes me feel like a celebrity living in Beverly Hills with how well they take care of you from the second you walk in. I always leave feeling confident in my dental health. Highly recommend to anyone looking for top-notch dental care!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tina Luu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXEjg5t1wcN1z0tn0WRjZk2YEVz_rJvMm69HDuWuTKEM28fA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son and I had our six-month dental cleaning appointment at Mukilteo Dental yesterday, and we had a wonderful experience.  Dr. Tiffany Luu-Tran is professional, gentle, kind, and very thorough.  She took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure we were both comfortable throughout the visit.\nHer dental assistants were wonderful also. They are friendly, gentle, and attentive, which made the appointment smooth and stress-free.  The entire team creates a welcoming and caring environment that truly shows how much they value their patients.\nWe always leave feeling well taken care of and confident in our dental care. Highly recommend Dr. Tiffany Luu-Tran and the team at Mukilteo Dental!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
