,"Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ho fit my son in for a dental emergency last year - sooo appreciate it.  I came in for my first dental cleaning with them today.  Amy at the front desk - super friendly - great smile that puts you at ease.  Dr. Ho did the initial consult portion - made sure he had all my info correctly, checked over my teeth and made sure nothing hurt.  Super friendly.  Then I got my teeth cleaned by Carter - literally the gentlest cleaning I've had.  He really took his time, being very careful to do a good job - but I pretty much felt nothing the whole time.  So if you've had dental cleaning trauma in the past, Carter can fix that.  100% recommend them to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonson Jiang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ2kZCGW-_IAPKhB_7_cwl4kEsRFp7rm8XOW5m22om1N-3h7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a filling and crown done here, and the experience was outstanding. The procedure was smooth, painless, and handled with great precision. Dr. Ho is very friendly and highly professional, making me feel comfortable and well cared for throughout the entire visit. I truly appreciate the quality of work and attention to detail.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Seo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-KfyGhXB6DXWK2jcAXWX2ylEo53iqMjGJU7N5M3Nv7KezQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Moved to Shoreline three years ago and tried to find a dentist. Changed couple of times, but I've never enjoyed with Dr. Ho and his crews' service. Drive back and forth about 1 hour from home, but this is absolutely good choice. 120% recommended if you are looking for a dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Craig Gardiner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6FxAbLK-PkQQqWBvg0FgPROduzNJusC3vmASgY8fh3iKKTnOI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Forum Dental is amazing. Everyone there is so friendly and customer service oriented. Highly recommend. Dr Ho and staff are awesome.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Suman Reddy Daida","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAFCvVCVpqGYprw1GQ3z30YQiYOVgVatz1xNJxlNdiQTNgh463=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have been there just to get filling done and not sure if the procedure was done wrong or the tools used were not hygienic but it created unbearable inflammation for 2 weeks and even after a month i still have inflammation and pain the only suggestion given is to get the root canal done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eleni Jimenez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyOS12CEIuz-Q0tzI0Ucd03VDUlLNB4-APDBaqRBhBU8t9JbQt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Dr. LaMarche and the whole team at Forum! They take great care of my family’s teeth, even my kiddos like going for cleanings. Highly recommend them if you are looking for a dentist!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0dhGV5Jat4iAOiZOHZZH4EpaCi0Qtq3wOafCBr6RpWlXBf8De-0vfA8_34YuKLTYv8blCwwxjazUS8wm7fgJ2r0kiaZiZtRjuuAf2hc5bNc-YuPOb6TvCh7qCiXJEb55mIPjX2Ig=k-no"],"When":"2022-4-28"},{"Name":"Justin Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKfMIhRmDBpwRs-VKpS6vjuEVoH7oW6qKY6grxTtfSq-mQC8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Ho is the best dentist in town. I had very complex dental issues, and I am incredibly grateful for the excellent care I received in such a short time. Dr. Ho is highly knowledgeable about all aspects of dental health, which saved me from the hassle of searching for multiple specialists. I am so grateful for his exceptional dental work. The caring and courteous staff also made my experience even better. I highly recommend Dr. Ho for anyone looking for top-notch dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gigi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnEYlgl8xZ6m7LwTIuRELHwnygiK6YIY3SGggISU2P4TLfCw=s120-c-