yl Ebner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLNL3AHG6rmORkHupkuI-l7BZBeud14QCV3iWZMRbFYAwGrSU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had gum line fillings. The process was so easy and comfortable.  Now my sensitivity is GONE!  Dr Singh did a great job job and I love having Roberto as the dental assistant. So dental and kind.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lulu Komanya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWPCjuSx4FgLeMEZJ7nzYRyxne4NBbn7ee_evj9IAOH74gbYzXmg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a very good experience. The staff was friendly, the appointment ran on time, and the dentist explained everything clearly, which helped reduce anxiety. I appreciated the attention to comfort and professionalism. people and very good service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarunya M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFuAsR2t4UvOLrdPeWNkH_ulUKUx7QrblMDPlZ3Pb3inqdi0EK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Singh is my favorite! The front desk team are always professional and friendly. I came in for a routine teeth cleaning, and it was one of the most comfortable and efficient cleanings I’ve ever had by Debbie! Dr. Singh is very professional, kind and takes the time to explain everything, and clearly cares about his patients comfort and dental health. I don’t like the dentist chair, but this team makes me feel comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Baneen A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJ47P9AA3I_3-WfnjTf8mW9uo-DhlEIQwTojsMeH5lUjsN48A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Singh and his team were amazing! I came in for a routine teeth cleaning, and it was one of the most comfortable and efficient cleanings I’ve ever had. Dr. Singh is very professional, takes the time to explain everything, and clearly cares about his patients comfort and dental health. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kevin Harris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFO0Mf4RVd54uSw73BNMog5TnWHqWbBjEwcnQsmqFGVrxfNcZ0hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed an urgent root canal and temporary crown the week going into the Holidays and they got me in right away. I’m a new patient here and they helped me with such great care that I’m going to stay with them for future visits. I just got the crown put in and I couldn’t be happier!\nI am incredibly happy and grateful for all of you here! Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanessa Rodriquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMDRDUpFb97FR4jRZUr6GVWX_52c22u8dHLwBfZTzCWZ0H_n0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don't love going to the dentist but for a place that tortures me every time I go there because they have to , they make the experience as pleasurable as possible . Everyone is kind and i have no issues with anything from the front to the hygienist and the dentist , all are great.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Leland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkzbYLDIJvgPT7i3Rl8Bp3MuDxAgmR2yLwlQf2lNtfOxDHoA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a fantastic dental experience this is! Friendly service from the front desk through the dental assistants and the dentist themselves. They patiently explain the procedures, detail what the dental care plan is for the future and generally make sure that you know what's going on. Our whole family goes here and I would recommend them for yours as well!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
