"When":""},{"Name":"Zoe Daniels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-f5OuUrHqqKrZCtM8tVzb_YEC6MkI6iJIFWw2vEwRtRB-fw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Cleaning and radiographs were pretty standard, nothing major to note. Dr didn't spend a lot of time going over treatment plan or doing an exam. I was scheduled for 2 cavity fillings several weeks after that first appointment as that was their first available appointment. I had an extremely poor experience with that filling appointment. I was given so much novacaine that I became light headed, dizzy and my heart was racing, I've had lots of fillings done and this has never happened before. The Dr and assistant were pulling on my mouth in opposite directions during the procedure to the point that it was causing pain that made me wince. The entire appointment felt rushed, the Dr spoke to me very little and was somewhat rude to the assistant. I ended up having to return to have them adjust the filling on my back molar as it was too high, after doing adjustments and saying it still felt off I was basically told there was nothing more they could do and it would \"wear down over time\". I also pointed out that there was a large gap in my teeth that wasn't there previously where they did the second filling and was dismissed as a non-concern. I got a second opinion and it turns out that non-contacting teeth is a concern and ultimately had to have that gap restored and the filling replaced less than a year later. The only reason I'm giving 2 stars is because the front desk staff is great. I would strongly recommend seeing another dentist for any sort of cavity work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"W01588 SA","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVHdGwbvOZUE9bmlay3biFnYCwA8yCWP8R_Uyapn4ruIUjew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you want honest and reliable dental care, Evergreen Family Dental is the place to go! Their team is so nice and friendly. Going to the dentist is never fun but they truly care about your comfort and experience.\nKatie B","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rita Johan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfHXhSTJut9nrII1vascF7SMytvlpU5cMJ8G2UNVLk-qPx9jSH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at this dental office. My hygienist, Mel, was excellent—gentle, thorough, and very knowledgeable. She took the time to explain everything and made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire visit. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adam Thorp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjr513PDPYFDva6joTXqdBZf0xPGCzCBGmklfpz3a_u5ibLsUxRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been coming here for several years. Dr Kim is the best dentist I’ve ever known and I have had extensive dental work done over the years by him.  We even changed insurance coverage in order to keep coming to this office. I highly recommend. The front desk staff are also very friendly (shoutout to Stephanie!).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Max Kviatkouski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZhPBGAzO1CArrueZQsa_1MiRcI0r4pfBJme_4nATiAUSCF6N5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love it here, that's why I keep coming back. Whole team is really caring and attentive. Every visit is a happy one. And I trust Dr. Kim's professional opinion on the best care options for me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cherix Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVerkhTI2bVkRUlMsHtCwa9cHOZrs0XKusKTm4-j3LrMhK29Z0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love this place. Everyone is so professional and friendly. I have had two crowns and a root canal done with Dr. Kim and very happy with the results. Christina the dental hygienist is my favorite person on this planet. I see her twice a year and I leave with a bigger brighter smile every time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy Nimaeva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQNXXXAwhfAOZmI0Ev_A9AYem1QlRuYcix35RAOiUxidQeQOpJ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dental office with great staff! I walked in terrified and walked out wondering why I didn’t come sooner. The staff is so friendly they made me forget someone was about to poke around my mouth with sharp tools. My teeth are sparkling, my anxiety is gone, and I’m basically ready for a toothpaste commercial. Five stars!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
