ebit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Nate Gardner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW8OXm7ZQgmn9hYT1nQYILEthJ6ICrIz36RMKnJU2yJny5HiYiliA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife recently moved to the US and needed a dentist. After researching online, we chose Lynnwood Dental Studio. They did a great job. They explained all the costs upfront in detail as soon as the diagnosis was known. No surprises, above and beyond breaking down the costs, explaining insurance coverage, and listing alternatives. Dr. Chintala provided a clear diagnosis and management plan, explained exactly what she recommended doing and why, and performed all the work quickly and precisely. She takes informed consent seriously and overall provided a great experience. They were very accommodating of our 2-year-old daughter as well, which put us at ease and let us focus on the dental work. Great dental clinic! My wife and I are happy we found a dentist for both of us.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chinmayee Patil","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ18qyBSHTTfocBjx6BYQP-lLUbvT1Dpt36Vf6wKS0ODpI3pA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Chintala was really helpful and took the time to explain everything clearly. I appreciated how thoroughly she went over my options and guided me on the next steps, which made the whole experience feel comfortable and stress-free. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gina Matlean","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_07plbZOoPCMc3h7JD0KCdnTR4Od8a3drb5RZ_eUcF2ksaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have anxiety going to the dentist, but my visit at Lynnwood Dental Studio was amazing. The staff at the front desk was very accommodating and helpful. The dental assistant was very gentle, calm and helpful in easing my pain and anxiety. The clinic is very clean and the soft music is calming to my nerves. Dr. Chantal was very gentle and made me feel comfortable during the whole procedure. I highly recommend it and would definitely come back for my future dental health needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derrick Stark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwqnxw97PhU-3tLiRnzbgKpqvSS8FyUX0KpIvRgTovKHEq1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Chantala was a life saver for me in a critical situation by agreeing to take me in that same day and masterfully performed the procedure that I came in for. I was nervous at times but she helped get me through it and I felt more comfortable. There was clear communication about what to expect and the pricing was more than fair. I only paid a copay, another dentist tried to charge me $1300 for the exact same procedure. I would recommend this place to friends and family because these people here are so nice and genuine. They make you feel at home.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Demaray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ54PjnTEuhh55u347YmXQwaQ2bPDDMYJMr0QBJax3myI2ZzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were very very helpful and very caring about my dental situation and made it a priority to help me in my time of need. Definitely very knowledgeable and very professional. I would highly recommend them to anybody that needs a caring dentist and somebody that they can trust to do a very good job. Very pleased their service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal Otey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLpCtsH75CjqLKYSxDSD2aSHeNSxwqqlReVxZo33tq5I5rRFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Do not come here!! Bad customer service, terrible at keeping records straight, won’t communicate properly with clients and will scam you!! I tried to be seen here for an extraction and never even made it into the chair. Never sent instructions beforehand, then tried to blame me when I asked about it, turns out they put someone else’s information into my file. Argued and belittled me when I got there, kept saying things weren’t offered even though it’s offered on their website. They also tried to say I may need to be on antibiotics for a few days before they could removed anything, which is a flat out lie and a way to make me pay more for something that should’ve been a single appointment. All around terrible dentist and I highly recommend finding anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Madison Hight","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyv5peU6H_ZmMq0Au7UOO4OKuMI3io6OnxlQNAcNcbrCRDjsld=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been visiting this practice for years now and appreciate the friendliness and quick service of the staff. I’m especially grateful for the noise cancelling headphones they offer during dental work. Thank you for keeping my teeth healthy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Perry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsgilTtM48hOjoDXlH0AlfFpOTl5_sJT-V5LgRdevC-6JVzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They were absolutely great.  I was having significant dental issues and they saw me immediately and took care of my symptoms.  I would highly recommend them for any dental issues.  They were very kind and caring.  I am very anxious when it comes to going to the dentist but all the personnel made me feel cared for and I was less anxious.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
