.com/a-/ALV-UjX9Ya0OZPgD152hBmngJCexSKZlOTYa4vyQcdLDq9kS1TFPHzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another fun visit at the Dentist.... you read that right!  The staff are all so nice yet very well trained and organized that my wife and I actually enjoy our visits. That coming from someone that has a laundry list of bad experiences with dentists is really saying something. If you want to look and feel better then Hamamoto 's is where to be.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beau Richards","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKWBULmV9zhbT_qx5o__8WTZ1HeAgTIZOgt_X4eLQc97l8SQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone here was friendly, professional, and easy to talk to. They did an excellent job of breaking everything down and explaining my options clearly in a way I could actually understand. The whole visit felt relaxed and welcoming. I left feeling well-informed and confident about my dental care. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chanille Schuster","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj5HSFU-eABRWlQ73eLkK59_HnHPhFXGVrTOaXe_ltyilRNc3f6w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 would recommend. Every single person in the office I came into contact with was so nice, caring and helpful. I really felt valued as a person, they listened to me, constantly checked on how I was doing during my procedure. I have nothing but good things to say. I usually do not enjoy going to the dentist but I can say I can't wait to go back next week for my check up.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy Shephard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUi2WEGWknbIiFd3WCKf1KgkZbxD4jmEK5qtJZDECGStAqtSUdG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I started with this dentist last week since my regular dentist is booked so far out. This turned out being a huge win for me. I’ve never had such a thorough exam. When my last dentist told me that there was not a lot of hope for my genetic bone loss and that I’d inevitably lose my teeth, these folks said, hold on! You just need deep cleaning every three months. They also found teeth that could be spared with crowns. From the very first phone call with Margie, on a Saturday mind you, to the greeting by Jessica at reception, to the exam by Dr. Stephanie and Leah, to the cleaning by Ivy, I have been treated very well and the work is outstanding!  They are a fun group; light hearted, but very efficient. I can’t express how grateful I am to have found them. This is my new Dentist office ☺️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hoda Tahami","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-gL167hyGu_fSKgmFiFh4G_RhzYVJnq5IA3yLs8yoYV_AuPfSDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I have been patients at Hamamoto Dentistry since early 2024 and have consistently received outstanding care. Our children also visit for their dental needs, and the team does a fantastic job making them feel comfortable and at ease.\nOne of the standout aspects of Dr. Hamamoto and the entire team is their thorough treatment planning. They take the time to discuss all dental concerns in detail, allowing us to plan for necessary treatments well in advance. The ability to plan treatments over time has been incredibly helpful, both from a health and financial perspective.\nDr. Hamamoto is not only highly skilled and professional but also genuinely caring. She takes the time to explain procedures, answer questions, and make sure we are comfortable with every step of the process. The entire staff, from the front desk to the dental hygienists and assistants, is exceptionally professional, friendly, and compassionate. They go above and beyond to create a welcoming environment, ensuring that each visit is as smooth and stress-free as possible.\nWe feel incredibly fortunate to have found such a trustworthy and excellent dental practice for our whole family. If you are looking for a dedicated, professional, and caring dental team, I wholeheartedly recommend Hamamoto Dentistry!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"scott Sackinger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNwtKTaGFXkAM0B5DuosUr4jkn-axqyY6sKScnLwIxESMgOY_C=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a well run Dental office. I’ve been a patient for ten years and consistently had excellent service and no wait. Very happy with this establishment.  The staff is consistently pleasant and always glad to see you.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3GVLXezFZ3-_803erihjXX5VNPDA8gjfNpUqb5sK80jhR7lQIGpG7DCEZE7C_0VtrbcdVlTKdk-v1cnW2Spssxx4y-GpJ3Z12TlO7a_UHnMBJmCA-YjqDtM9HI8ntrU2-Vnn0=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3GYrmyckbfdvd-J2KaPlQMNr7KlES-BLuE0LcXedXOGQZdNYytSO-w5DHunLC0DHBcl3MLrak21vUvkFXy5qjpHIm281NGa2CmOOKPABDZA0QeP6YimwIuiOqn1ozFr5oGCgjCHA=k-no"],"When":"2023-11-17"},{"Name":"Terry Duran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCRdIirC4KqMhnxlnoFlHi2NJnPxnioE_hKyvYVPsLlLZQtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot applaud the entire crew at Hamamoto Dentistry enough. Absolutely every member of the team is extraordinary. They truly care about their patients \u0026 their professionalism is outstanding. Hats off to the incredible dentist, most helpful manager, cheerful receptionist, \u0026 a most competent crew. They totally go above \u0026 beyond every step of the way \u0026 I cannot recommend them enough. Looking for a new dentist? Try Hamamoto Dentistry. You'll be happy you did. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVABA4FhZcpUpPK4AucSWnC1vTR2ltfyP1zFuljULYm-90cQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've really appreciated the quality care I have received at Hamamoto Dentistry. Everyone there is incredibly nice and professional. Their treatment plans have always been tailored toward what is best for me rather than what is best for their bottom lines.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
