1/thumbnail?panoid=i71pDUzr2OP6QdV5mRMWbg\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=282.79053\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://book.modento.io/c/b2a364bb1bc5454ba32945bffd5025fe/website/patient-details","source":"modento.io"},{"link":"https://www.drwagnerdds.com/contact_us/","source":"drwagnerdds.com"}],"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://www.drwagnerdds.com/dental-services/\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwiF0ZHKk9CUAxUSEzQIHV8XHnMQqRkIHygS\u0026usg=AOvVaw1Fqa-AWT6OVzAdh52qJHum","source":"drwagnerdds.com"},"owner":{"id":"107427817710238027886","name":"Wagner Family Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107427817710238027886"},"complete_address":{"borough":"West Ridge","street":"12625 NE 173rd Pl","city":"Woodinville","postal_code":"98072","state":"Washington","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Brian Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK2QNgsWZVsTLFvnK3GGNqhVQZV_YkWPPXu6etLpCFvWqHUeQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been to several different dentists around Washington and never quite found one I felt fully comfortable with until I came to Wagner Family Dentistry.\n\nDr. Wagner is extremely skilled, and that confidence shows the moment he starts working. From a routine cleaning to fixing a crown, everything was done carefully, efficiently, and with great attention to detail. It’s honestly the first time in a long while that I felt relaxed in the dental chair.\n\nThe office staff is just as impressive. They are friendly, professional, and organized. They made the entire experience easy and comfortable from start to finish, which is not something I’ve been able to say about other dental offices in the area.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dentist in Washington who is highly skilled, trustworthy, and backed by a fantastic team, I can’t recommend Wagner Family Dentistry enough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gina Thayer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXawkTDX4ezYaL9ZlTxT_M5NFUBbeizP_QoRXAE13g-N1KMnYh5wA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Wagner and his entire office were so warm and welcoming. It’s hard to find a practitioner in any field these days who can put your mind at ease, make you feel calm and relaxed all while providing non judgmental and educated advice.\nKarly was my dental hygienist. She greeted me with a smile and easy going conversation. She was gentle and kind and offered great feedback and options. I highly recommend trying Wagner Family Dentistry for you and your whole family!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Monroe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJaTS7gms08CH0A_cz80wmKUL4AYGkLIbgxPTqVHOu9O3Nhg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Looked for a new dentist close to home since our last dentist retired. Called the office and had an appointment in less than 2 weeks. They also put me on the call list if they had a cancellation and 2 days later they called and I had my 1st visit 2 days later. The staff are very warm and friendly. They explain in great detail the services offered and what that entails. The hygienist I saw was very detailed with everything that would take place. She was warm and friendly and very informative as she took the x-rays. She showed me areas that were of concern. She worked quickly and was very gentle. Dr. Wagner is also warm and friendly. He went over the x-rays and set up a course of treatment. It’s very obvious this office cares about their patients. I’m looking forward to a longstanding relationship with Wagner Family Dentistry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Travis Burch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXrIgForevSaUdSI8TGwtJBKUgIyglIx_ijKgaUGpwmC4F6SvsG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you live in the Woodinville or surrounding areas you owe it to yourself to find a dental team that takes care of your needs and is always warm and welcoming, as dental health is an important and often overlooked area of care.\n\nFrom the minute I stepped into office for my first exam and cleaning; I’ve received nothing but world class customer care. Dr. Wagner and the team have always given me my options and recommendations for next treatment steps; and taken care of anyone that I’ve recommended stop by their offices. I’m proud to say I’ve found my dentist for as long as I call Washington my home.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqoVDkF_Wxw4XiN-nfwIspW2O5nSuPSxisCXOaPjqhaJnNd8tY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was so so nervous coming in as a fruit snack betrayed me and ripped my crown off over the holidays and unfortunately my  tooth came with it and was not salvageable. It had been a few years since I had been to the dentist which had my anxiety through the roof but everyone welcomed me in and never once made me feel uncomfortable or embarrassed about my teeth. Genuinely a wonderful experience. Every interaction was warm and friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josiah Simpkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKXOtgpjqY_XWZXvPIGkc72L1t8Bp0QvCv6VQwK6BU7SA0FaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Incredibly professional and welcoming. Made comfort and care their top priority as well and full transparency. I would highly recommend this practice to anyone looking for a new dentist. Thank you so much!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lachlan Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxcj-Izxp8SvaDeydxqH0vWbhv4Z4V1WJfPvP8NbB9CnjcsuEoxA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist I've ever been too! Super fun and professional at the same time. If your looking for a good dentist that actually cares this one is perfect.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheri Holley-Reyla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLeMbXHgsWuh-maRldnLIoo8OOfskZZw74qMzaK_aELG0A4ng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m not the biggest fan of going to the dentist, but I do faithfully every six months! Dr Wagner office makes it so easy to make that cleaning appointment as I know when I am there I feel very comfortable, and know they all care! Never have I had a bad experience! Thank you all for everything!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
