escription":"10/10 experience. The dentist is very kind \u0026 explained things very well. You can tell they actually care about your health \u0026 aren’t just trying to make a buck. As someone who works in the dental field, I appreciated so much about this office! Brenda was an amazing assistant, made sure I was comfortable \u0026 did her job very well. The front desk \u0026 hygienist were all wonderful too! No complaints here. Thanks for taking good care of me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIF6fSuqYfTeZi8ucA_WOM_xoM146K4U8lZe1FU2RXd7YL8mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming to WEDental for years even as I have moved around the area because Dr. Fred and his staff are amazing! They are caring, will answer all your questions, and are considerate even during less than fun procedures. I plan to continue to visit Dr. Fred for many years to come.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mukesh Kathayat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQPJ98WCoYfaHynZ4JC8WhCbiECirUQsswD1q1RSdo7MEAkMoQ_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ashley the front lady is rude not helpfull and didn't gave me accurate information about coverage and out of pocket cost.I paid my copay evrytime at the time of service but they surprised me after couple of months sending different amounts of bill. They are not giving us the correct information about the coverage. I live near by this dental facility that's why i go here but not anymore going here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jer Ruck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJd17zJ74hgJsi_MvS1ecyN6XZJdUevaQ05nmmd5JiSRxdTQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everything was amazing! Best dental experience I can remember! The scheduling desk was kind and accomodating. Karla was very warm and excellent at cleaning without any pain. Cami was phenomenal and thorough as a hygienist and also very personable. Dr. Fred was so patient and warm and wanted to really take time to get to know me and any concerns I may have had. I don't write many reviews, but these guys deserve it!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dene Warren Sakamoto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpgsVN-EDQa4EmPlup6mHDfVBg0cxLj6ZBeSxC3dhzns68eg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really appreciate the patient care at WeDental with Dr. Worrell.  Not uncommon but I too suffer greatly from anxiety esp when going to the dentist. Even for routine checkup. Dr. Worrell has always been patient with me and knowing about my anxiety treats me well with regards to easing my anxiety during procedures. The staff are also excellent with patient care; the hygienist to the other dental assistants and front desk. I appreciate their excellent customer service.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
