e},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking garage","enabled":true},{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_h7w8vDtjTx9jL-D6eFjyeo2EGEincP9opN5OZhBlckw5dw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dentist truly exceeded my expectations. He was kind, professional, and very thorough during my dental wellness check. I appreciated being shown detailed images and having everything explained clearly so I could fully understand my options.\nThe technology in the office made the experience feel transparent and informative. I never felt pressured — just well-informed and respected. Communication was smooth, and the overall experience felt organized and thoughtful.\nI would absolutely recommend this office to family and friends. It’s clear they prioritize quality care and patient education.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Pranger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl7F2IIMmIimr34AykPn_RhSlqfh13ljQ01ikTiQ_kHXkrR_17=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The intake process online for setting up an appointment was very direct and efficient and did not require a phone call. They responded to my texts within minutes and I got scheduled right away. There’s no stress of loud or overwhelming waiting room chaos since you go in right at your appointment time. The Dr was very calm, direct and informative which helped me manage my anxiety. I appreciated the methods used to clean my teeth as the process was relatively painless and better than cleanings I’ve had before. Honestly the whole process exceeded my expectations and I would definitely recommend this place to my friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wendy Schevers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvSxB84-HLDtxP0pc3GlCX0VfFZys8TtZGowBR-nMH_6y5fQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First of all, I was surprised at how quickly I was able to get an appointment. The receptionist and the dentist were both kind and professional. My cleaning went quickly and that was a relief. No pain at all. Then the dentist took some time to explain to me my options for going forward with my dental health. I was grateful for his kindness and suggestions.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D Z","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXhc0nyh_JJMoYqJJcCCA-1kWBlBLaNK-8Si66a1WBIpvrWg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an appointment at \"Affordable Family Dentistry\" and it was a great experience. I appreciate being able to text the office for scheduling. The team was very prompt in scheduling me and got me in during a lunch break. The office was very clean and Dr. Chiang was vey thorough, welcoming, and professional. I appreciate how informative he was towards my oral health. He explained the overall health of my teeth and jaw and gave me advice on how to take care of it in the long term. He also thoroughly answered all of my questions and concerns. I left feeling like I learned more from just a cleaning and x-ray.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A Dirini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPE72M3BxN_90odeJk78rsWM4BGS2zLckluBWlCVJbFAhmHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited “Affordable Family Dentistry “ for the first time, and I couldn’t be happier with the experience. The office environment was clean and welcoming. The front desk staff was friendly and efficient and made the check-in a breeze.  Dr. Chiang was very professional and thorough. He performed a comprehensive exam, took the time to discuss my X-rays and oral health in detail, and laid out a clear treatment plan without any pressure. I really appreciate the personalized approach and genuine care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abby Jacobo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-xLuI3Mz82hJyuR4nc1JvKc6uTJw9U7VLOhA71EdNHV6EyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at Affordable Family Dentistry. From the moment I walked in, the office was very clean and welcoming. The front desk staff were professional and kind, and I was able to get in and see the doctor quickly without a long wait.\n\nThe dentist was extremely professional and transparent about my care. He took the time to explain all of my options thoroughly, including the pros and cons of each, which I really appreciated. His honesty and clarity saved me so much time and helped me feel confident about my treatment decisions.\n\nOverall, this was one of the best dental visits I’ve ever had. The professionalism of both the staff and the dentist stood out, and I left feeling well cared for and informed. I will definitely be recommending Affordable Family Dentistry to friends and family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DazzleGod2619","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNrtmyDrBIIgqDd5j-CpjHdoOKj0B0j2IShIuW3ELASsZWJAU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dentist. In all my experience with dental providers, this clinic was nice and helpful. Gentle with cleaning teeth. My teeth barely hurt vs past cleanings from past dentists. Very informative and helpful. Answered all my concerns truthfully and to his best knowledge or opinion. Actually seemed to know new ways of caring for teeth vs old school. I like that. :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emanuel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxgTxfsQY2Rv8iMjs9PeTFZar4ZZpZhx45V70ZZBoeJWwbow=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had an old filling fall out and a piece of that same tooth break off. We called looking for a place that would take me in and Affordable Family Dentistry was able to accommodate us promptly.\n\nWhen I arrived, I was called back almost immediately. The Dentist was welcoming and kind. He did an x-ray with a fancy machine and then did a few more exams to get a more detailed assessment of my tooth.\n\nThe Dentist was extremely thorough in his examination, but also in his explanation. He was clear and specific which made me feel comfortable knowing I was in good hands. He would follow-up each of his points by asking if I had any questions and proceed to answer my questions in a way that was easy to follow. He took time to make me feel at ease, which I really appreciate.\n\nI would highly recommend Affordable Family Dentistry. Thank you for the great service!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
