eth and to monitor anything that looked concerning.  After many years with him, my teeth were in good shape.  Sadly, I had to move and can't find another diamond like him.  I highly recommend him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathleen Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIM9xydiOh2sapaP5BtnTwMLFz4tghQNTUyXtN5FcHsF0FONQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been here with both of my children (ages 4 and 2) and had a great experience. The Dentist is knowledgeable, the receptionist is very friendly and competent, the hygienist was more than accommodating for my sensitive teeth, and my kids had a good experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nick murray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULptTXUzPM42cCcAo-TgIi6QMwrH7YZAw43P7G_EkL2dVCl8J6=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic practice / team.  I'm generally uncomfortable at dentists but the team was great, took their time, and made sure I was comfortable throughout the process.  11/10 would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Josh Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQEkUU4rvOrsOHqwA5orisQIH1wP9X5VpX1le6G5Li8a30U5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Misleading should put hours when available to not waste time calling if it’s past normal  business hours.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey Herrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6_JdWNKG7aDfywblDuRLHl2gIWOhlD69WyFYZi6Ks0H1bK3HP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Im not one to write reviews, but this place is great. I have severe anxiety surrounding the dentist, and they do everything they can to make the experience feel safe and keep you informed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"T D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZJr0OKKpiL4c_BDaQY2bM9QbiBW5P7j8Z_8iyYt67KL4tVBU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very nice people here