":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Edison De Impala","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImh8szt2EBBfcM5laUazCHuG5uHkSG1pHyWeuU02_EHCH2NA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Icon Dental in Everett for the past four years, and I’ve had a really great experience. Everyone in the office is always friendly, welcoming, and professional, which makes every visit feel easy and comfortable. I’ve received excellent orthodontic care from Dr. Sohrabi, and his expertise truly stands out. He is incredibly skilled, detail-oriented, and precise, and I’ve always felt confident in the care and results he provides. I’ve also received excellent general dental care from Dr. Aboulhosn and Dr. Kwok, who are both kind, professional, and thorough. Overall, I’ve always felt like I’m in very good hands at Icon Dental, and I definitely recommend them to anyone looking for high-quality dental care and a great team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Olivia Kemp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUoofqeyUJMyPsJHYUv6klEN2SKV6Xg-tq9Q_0eVvdNz_duYHIL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been at Icon Dental for the last few years and have consistently seen Dr. Kwok since 2023. I have ALWAYS had dentist angst but since coming to Icon even prior to Dr. Kwok, it is gone. The team is incredible. From the moment you walk in, the sweet receptionist/coordinator knows your name and throught the multiple Drs/Othos/hygentists I’ve seen, the approach is the same. The patient experience comes first. Dr. Kwok is an actual angel. She listens, takes me along in my care and ensure I understand what she is doing, always greets with a (masked) smile on her face, pays attention to the details, and makes going to the dentist feel like a warm hug (as warm as a dentist can be) vs a cold hour of pure stress. On top of it all, I have the most admiration for how she treats the dental assistants. She is their partner, teacher, and cheerleader, not their intimidating boss. As someone who visits a lot of medical professionals, this is so rare. The world needs  more Dr. Kwoks!\n\nI live far from Icon now and I will always come back to Dr. Kwok!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Art Tygert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLnxvfJPK9vFyVcwmclAHXHZMBV4hL5-EqI3CPhjzNj7GtgFt83Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had a consistently positive experience with Icon Dental in Everett, WA over the past two years. Dr. Kwok and the entire team are professional, welcoming, and genuinely caring.\n\nEven when there’s a sign that says “We’ll be back at X time,” there is always someone nearby ready to help, greet you with a smile, and get you checked in. The team dynamic is excellent. You can hear them communicating clearly with one another, which is critical in a healthcare setting.\n\nI highly recommend Dr. Kwok and the entire Icon Dental team!! *****","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"manish shakya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaPzjnjwTg7YEY-nuc7HVpEmhcO_d1L4OptbBGbUjEs1U0TA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Warning: Avoid this clinic. Last year, I was told a deep cleaning was required and mostly covered by my insurance. After completing half the treatment, I was hit with a massive bill and told it wasn't covered. Even though it was their mistake, they threatened me with collections until I paid in full. To make matters worse, they promised I would qualify for the rest of the treatment after November and said they would call me—I never received that call. They are quick to demand money but fail to follow through on their word. Stay away.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Hegge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwU2N2XScrOrCqRnxuAvcsivqzhcti0I1h_8okUYKAfBk6anc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My complete experience at Icon Dental Everett has been nothing short of exceptional. The front desk staff were friendly, helpful, polite, and accommodating. I initially came to Icon Dental to determine whether my wisdom teeth were ready for removal due to some irregular aches and pains. Dr. Aboulhosn not only recommended a full dental exam on the spot, but also made extra time in her busy morning to personally complete my exam before scheduling me for a deep cleaning.\n\nMy deep cleaning appointment was truly phenomenal. Every one of my concerns (especially given my history of poor and painful dental experiences) was addressed with care and thoughtful solutions. The direct care I received from Dr. Aboulhosn and her team was outstanding. I would highly recommend Icon Dental Everett, and especially Dr. Aboulhosn, for all your personal and family dental needs or if you simply want the best in the business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Art Tygert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI85XAqubt2_zbZXionDSfsY4WWnv-sZ5E9pigAFLXTl-6MOirF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had a consistently positive experience with Icon Dental in Everett, WA over the past two years. Dr. Kwok and the entire team are professional, welcoming, and genuinely caring.\n\nEven when there’s a sign that says “We’ll be back at X time,” there is always someone nearby ready to help, greet you with a smile, and get you checked in. The team dynamic is excellent. You can hear them communicating clearly with one another, which is critical in a healthcare setting.\n\nI highly recommend Dr. Kwok and the entire Icon Dental team!! *****","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0NzOXgCZwzMz8_WYjAgiDf_359iMmlkoqwivCREvUSq7uopFLaut8FPa6wOb0fROnMGaTpgBFqNBY890fgnh6NrS0_-fNIEVN0OHTkLpVv7vxdHxCkFPj-cHgsgx1rxFC2hKVd97uHNzY=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-12"},{"Name":"G G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMWWun7lwf9bNelAqVg6D9EMaqLPUjd0YkjXIr_B7hBjJ_vA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really great staff. I've been here three times, and everyone is honestly lovely. My teeth are a mess due to low income/poor access to affordable dental in a small town before moving here. No one shamed me like some dentists. Very happy with service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sebastian Cobb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVP_x40v6XiZEDXbSzs9dnT6MbRMyDOai04R-wHI_hsFBGRYSQp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The whole staff is so sweet and caring, they put your care above everything else. I have been nervous to restart my Dental care. They have made every ensurance to make it comfortable, friendly and supportive.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
