ol for a few days because my mouth hurts so bad. Not here! Not at Snohomish Family Dentistry. I highly recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelby Fischer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKS0geabYKGvAHUaVPOPmRzX_34mYfgWKKXsLH5fQJOvv-m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came here after having a bad experience at another dentist for a Second opinion. Absolutely love the dentist. He was so funny and put me at ease made the dentist not so scary for someone that doesn't like the dentist and confirmed my suspicion that my previous dentist was recommending things that weren't needed. Can't wait to switch my whole family over.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Natalie Gaceta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6iZhuU50LY6n4OxNhjCqyC-YU5dLYbVk7E8XQByPeTVueCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am beyond grateful for this place. Long story short I got my wisdom teeth removed at a different dentist and after 5 weeks of no answers to why I was experiencing intense jaw pain, I went to snoho family dental for a second opinion. Dr gwak was extremely thorough, checked everything, explained everything in detail to me and he explained to me I was experiencing nerve damage, which I wish my original dentist would have told me in the first place to save me from weeks of anxiety about what was happening to my mouth. The level of care snohomish family dentistry has is amazing, I genuinely feel like they care about my health. I decided to switch to here as my regular dentist. I’m so thankful for them","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Flipp G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIelu7rW87lUucfp3U9BwG-1Z1WfU4k5S60Xg8WbEtOS8qH2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best Dentistry Ive ever been to!\nDr. Jiwon Gwak and his assistant Andrea was Amazing! I've been to , two other dentistries and I can tell you the team moves fast ,but very smooth going!\nDr.Jiwon Gwak extracted two teeth under a minute and I did not FEEL a thing!\nSnohomish Family Dentistry is the perfect place to visit if your having oral issues!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcia Thumma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvpwZ0X-Af2Mn8ag9CzGzGic7ndnR5yd5-aoRzgpEoCwwWMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit here. Everything about the visit was positive and I will definitely return!  The front office staff are friendly and professional. The hygienist was concerned about my comfort, constantly communicating with me as she worked, and was a very warm, cheerful professional as well.  The dentist was very personable, also very happy and very professional! A+ on all fronts.  Very easy people to work with!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stasia Porter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkpTXoZqB7du7o-3FcY_rh3Wz_7ZhcouUEfknBuGcIrea6gWGKYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just love everyone at this office, from the front desk to the hygienists to the wonderful Dr. Gwak! he and his team are helping me be healthy and I've never been so happy to go to the dentist before! I bring my child to him, too. He and his team are the very, very best! Friendly and comfortable and great, great people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hope Kocan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXwP6bVBrlK31UACU2beiv616TBWNBuTXAhACu40hZn-rlp5WYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love Snohomish Family Dentistry! I'm very excited for my next appointment!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
